0%E2%80%9CBJP%20has%20started%20sending%20invitations%20with%20%E2%80%98Republic%20of%20Bharat%E2%80%99%20instead%20of%20%E2%80%98Republic%20of%20India%E2%80%99.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CArticle%201%20of%20the%20Constitution%20reads%20%E2%80%98India%20that%20is%20Bharat%E2%80%99.%20Neither%20you%20will%20be%20able%20to%20take%20India%20from%20us%20nor%20Bharat.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENo%20official%20statement%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Pradhan%E2%80%99s%20tweet%20put%20speculation%20to%20rest%20about%20the%20dinner%20invitations%2C%20the%20entire%20day%20witnessed%20confusion%20amongst%20officialdom%20and%20even%20the%20BJP%2C%20with%20a%20scramble%20as%20no%20official%20statement%20had%20been%20made%20by%20the%20Rashtrapati%20Bhawan%20or%20the%20Ministry%20of%20External%20Affairs%20(MEA)%2C%20which%20is%20coordinating%20the%20G20%20events.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20asked%20about%20the%20authenticity%20of%20the%20invitation%20doing%20the%20rounds%20on%20social%20media%2C%20Rashtrapati%20Bhawan%20sources%20conveyed%20that%20G20%20events%20are%20being%20coordinated%20by%20the%20MEA%20and%20only%20they%20can%20respond%20on%20this.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20confirmed%20that%20the%20invitation%20card%20is%20genuine%20and%20such%20wording%20has%20been%20used%20for%20the%20second%20time.%20During%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20visit%20to%20Greece%20last%20month%2C%20all%20protocol%20material%20put%20out%20referred%20to%20the%20%E2%80%9CPrime%20Minister%20of%20Bharat%E2%80%9D%2C%20it%20is%20believed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20staff%20said%20that%20it%20has%20been%20orally%20told%20to%20use%20Bharat%20henceforth.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FPandaJay%2Fstatus%2F1698964637289517242%5C%22%3EBaijayant%20Panda%2C%20BJP%20national%20vice%20president%3C%2Fa%3E%20wrote%2C%20%E2%80%9CIt%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20take%20rocket%20science%20to%20comprehend%20this%2C%20yet%20Congress%20%26amp%3B%20AAP%20are%20opposing%20a%20G20%20invite%20by%20the%20President%20of%20Bharat.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20to%20wait%20and%20see%20if%20it%20will%20be%20a%20part%20of%20the%20Special%20Session%20(of%20Parliament)%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Union%20minister%20Rajeev%20Chandrashekhar%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FANI%2Fstatus%2F1698967504461472078%5C%22%3Eto%20ANI.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECongress%20MP%20Gaurav%20Gogoi%20said%20both%20Bharat%20and%20India%20were%20accepted%20names%20of%20the%20country%2C%20yet%20the%20BJP%20was%20presenting%20them%20in%20opposition%20to%20each%20other.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20accept%20both%20%E2%80%98India%E2%80%99%20and%20%E2%80%98Bharat%E2%80%99%20names%20and%20feel%20proud%20on%20them.%20The%20%E2%80%98I%E2%80%99%20in%20ISRO%20is%20India%2C%20the%20%E2%80%9CI%E2%80%9D%20in%20IITs%20is%20India%2C%20the%20%E2%80%98I%E2%80%99%20in%20IIMs%20is%20India%2C%20the%20%E2%80%98I%E2%80%99%20in%20IPS%20is%20India.%20The%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20politics%20has%20stooped%20so%20low%20because%20they%20are%20afraid%20of%20the%20INDIA%20(opposition)%20alliance%2C%E2%80%9D%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiatodayne.in%2Fnational%2Fstory%2Fbjp-has-stooped-low-as-they-are-afraid-of-india-alliance-congress-mp-gaurav-gogoi-673112-2023-09-05%5C%22%3Ehe%20said%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693910671000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F05161148%2FF5P-ZgaXAAEVAJK.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fpresident-of-bharat-g20-invitation%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Trying%20to%20scotch%20out%20the%20mention%20of%20India%2C%20the%20banquet%20card%20for%20G20%20hosted%20by%20the%20President%20of%20India%2C%20Droupadi%20Murmu%2C%20now%20describes%20her%20as%20'President%20of%20Bharat'.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fpres