%20after%20mastering%20ChatGPT.%20%3Cp%3EChris%20Winfield%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EChris%20Winfield%20owns%20a%20brand-coaching%20company%20helping%20small%20business%20and%20entrepreneurs.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHe%20discovered%20AI%20using%20Dall-E%20in%202021%20and%20later%20became%20enthralled%20by%20ChatGPT%20and%20other%20AI%20tools.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EBy%20selling%20AI%20products%20and%20using%20AI%20tools%2C%20Winfield%20made%20%242.7%20million%20in%20the%20last%206%20months.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20as-told-to%20story%20is%20based%20on%20a%20transcribed%20conversation%20with%20Chris%20Winfield%2C%20the%20owner%20of%20Super%20Connector%20Media%20and%20Understanding%20AI%2C%20that%20has%20been%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'd%20been%20in%20the%20public-relations%20business%20for%20eight%20years%20when%20I%20started%20experimenting%20with%20artificial-intelligence%20tools%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2FJasper.ai%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EJasper%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2FCopy.ai%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECopy.AI%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%202021.%20They%20could%20create%20copy%20that%20captured%20my%20brand%20voice%20for%20email%20newsletters%20and%20social%20media.%20I%20got%20excited%20and%20thought%2C%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20the%20coolest%20thing%20ever.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELittle%20did%20I%20know%20what%20was%20on%20the%20AI%20horizon.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBefore%20starting%20my%20company%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthesocialmediasellingsystem.com%2Fai-nv-web%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EUnderstanding%20AI%2C%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20which%20helps%20other%20business%20owners%20leverage%20AI%20tools%2C%20I%20owned%20a%20PR%20agency%20and%20brand-coaching%20company%20called%20Super%20Connector%20Media.%20I%20founded%20it%20with%20my%20partner%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fjengottlieb.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EJen%20Gottlieb%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20in%20March%202018.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHaving%20a%20PR%20agency%20was%20never%20my%20dream%2C%20so%20I%20sold%20the%20agency%20side%20in%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EI%20used%20my%20downtime%20to%20learn%20AI%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20remember%20when%20Dall-E%20was%20released%20last%20summer%2C%20my%20mind%20was%20blown.%20I%20could%20type%20something%20into%20the%20tool%2C%20and%20it%20made%20a%20picture%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0it%20felt%20unbelievable.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20no%20longer%20had%20to%20manage%20the%20agency%20and%20had%20more%20time%20on%20my%20hands%20to%20explore%20AI%20tools.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELater%2C%20that%20autumn%2C%20ChatGPT%20was%20released.%20I%20started%20experimenting%20with%20how%20to%20use%20it%20for%20Super%20Connector%20Media.%20At%20the%20time%2C%20our%20main%20focus%20was%20running%20personal-branding%20workshops.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20would%20ask%20ChatGPT%20to%20help%20me%20define%20our%20ideal%20client%20and%20write%20journal%20entries%20as%20that%20persona%2C%20then%20turn%20the%20journal%20entries%20into%20ad%20copy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20every%20hour%20I%20spent%20learning%20ChatGPT%2C%20it%20felt%20like%20I%20got%2040%20hours%20back.%20I%20had%20never%20used%20anything%20that%20could%20give%20me%20results%20that%20quickly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20started%20sharing%20what%20I%20was%20learning%20in%20late%202022%20on%20Facebook%20and%20via%20email%20with%20my%20audience%20of%20business%20owners%20and%20entrepreneurs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EPeople%20wanted%20to%20learn%20about%20generative%20AI%20but%20already%20felt%20behind%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ETalking%20with%20my%20audience%20via%20direct%20messages%20and%20market-research%20calls%2C%20I%20found%20that%20business%20owners%20who%20had%20yet%20to%20try%20ChatGPT%20felt%20overwhelmed.%20They%20thought%20AI%20was%20everywhere%20and%20they%20were%20already%20behind.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20knew%20AI%20could%20improve%20their%20businesses%20and%20workflow%20if%20they%20could%20overcome%20their%20fears.%20So%20Jen%20and%20I%20started%20teaching%20AI%20use%20cases%20for%20businesses%20via%20paid%20online%20challenges.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20ran%20our%20first%20challenge%20in%20January%20and%20had%20350%20customers.%20We%20promoted%20the%20challenges%20on%20social%20media%20and%20through%20our%20email%20lists%20of%20over%20120%2C000%20people%2C%20as%20well%20as%20with%20paid%20ads%20on%20Meta's%20platforms.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20started%20with%20a%20%2425%2C000%20advertising%20budget%20for%20challenges.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20a%20challenge%2C%20if%20someone%20wants%20more%20support%2C%20we%20offer%20courses%20and%20%26quot%3Bmastermind%26quot%3B%20programs%20that%20have%20prices%20in%20the%20four-figure%20range%20and%20in%20the%20low%20five%20figures%2C%20respectively.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20packages%20show%20people%20how%20to%20grow%20a%20profitable%20personal%20brand%20and%20business%20online%20using%20AI%20to%20streamline%20the%20business-building%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3ETeaching%20AI%20to%20our%20audience%20skyrocketed%20revenue%20and%20growth%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20now%20run%20six-figure%20ad%20campaigns%20per%20challenge%2C%20and%20over%2040%2C000%20people%20have%20paid%20to%20be%20part%20of%20our%20challenges%20in%20the%20past%20eight%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20we%20incorporated%20AI%20products%20in%20January%2C%20our%20revenue%20has%20jumped%20to%20%242.7%20million%20in%20sales.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20started%20Understanding%20AI%20with%20eight%20Super%20Connector%20team%20members%20and%20expanded%20to%2017%20to%20help%20with%20sales%2C%20ads%2C%20videos%2C%20and%20customer%20support.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20earn%20revenue%20by%20teaching%20people%20how%20to%20use%20AI%20tools%2C%20but%20we%20also%20use%20AI%20tools%20to%20maximize%20our%20revenue.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EHow%20I%20use%20AI%20to%20improve%20my%20own%20business'%20workflow%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20use%20ChatGPT%20to%20help%20create%20marketing%20material.%20AI%20generates%2080%25%20of%20the%20material%2C%20and%20my%20input%20is%20the%20remaining%2020%25.%20Sometimes%20I'll%20add%20more%20of%20my%20own%20voice.%20Other%20times%20I%20just%20change%20the%20headline.%20I%20always%20remind%20my%20clients%20that%20AI%20isn't%20a%20foolproof%20replacement%20for%20your%20brand%20voice.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOnce%20you've%20mastered%20one%20tool%2C%20you%20can%20build%20your%20AI%20stack.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20found%20memes%20work%20well%20in%20ads%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2FSupermeme.ai%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ES%3Cu%3Eupermeme.AI%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20helps%20you%20generate%20memes%20from%20text%20inputs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20uploaded%20ads%20recently%20with%20AI-generated%20memes%2C%20and%20they%20turned%20around%20a%20campaign%20that%20wasn't%20doing%20well.%20The%20ads%20we%20created%20with%20Supermeme%20lowered%20our%20cost%20per%20click%20by%2072%25.%20It's%20a%20tool%20that%20requires%20less%20than%201%25%20of%20my%20time%20but%20makes%20a%20big%20difference.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20spend%20between%20%245%2C000%20and%20%247%2C500%20monthly%20on%20AI%20tools.%20It%20varies%20based%20on%20how%20many%20tools%20I'm%20testing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20considering%20investing%20time%20in%20a%20new%20tool%2C%20I%20follow%20the%20rule%20of%20three.%20If%20I%20hear%20about%20a%20tool%20from%20three%20sources%20or%20people%20I%20trust%2C%20I%20will%20spend%20time%20looking%20into%20it.%20Otherwise%2C%20all%20the%20new%20AI%20tools%20can%20become%20just%20shiny%20objects.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'll%20then%20consider%20whether%20the%20tool%20would%20be%20helpful%20for%20my%20business%20and%20whether%20I%20can%20teach%20a%20lot%20of%20people%20to%20use%20it.%20I%20try%20to%20find%20tools%20that%20are%20relevant%20to%20small-business%20owners%20so%20I%20can%20teach%20them%20as%20part%20of%20my%20AI%20programs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3ESales%20AI%20nearly%20doubled%20our%20revenue%20between%20challenges%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwoosender.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWooSender%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20an%20AI-powered%20sales%20assistant%20that%20we've%20used%20since%20April.%20If%20someone%20applies%20for%20our%20%26quot%3Bmastermind%26quot%3B%20program%2C%20I%20can%20assign%20the%20lead%20to%20one%20of%20our%20two%20salespeople%2C%20and%20WooSender%20reaches%20out%20to%20the%20prospective%20customer%20as%20if%20it's%20the%20salesperson%20with%20on-brand%20messaging.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20tool%20automatically%20finds%20available%20times%20in%20the%20salesperson's%20calendar.%20If%20someone%20replies%20that%20they%20want%20to%20book%20the%20demo%2C%20it%20books%20the%20appointment%2C%20sends%20the%20calendar%20invite%2C%20and%20texts%20the%20person%20a%20confirmation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20we%20implemented%20WooSender%2C%20we%20did%20just%20under%20double%20the%20sales%20for%20the%20next%20challenge.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20July%2C%20we%20hired%20a%20second%20salesperson%20because%20our%20challenges%20were%20growing%20in%20popularity.%20AI%20has%20helped%20improve%20his%20close%20percentage.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBefore%20AI%20tools%2C%20you'd%20have%20to%20listen%20to%20hours%20of%20sales%20calls%20to%20give%20feedback.%20Now%20we%20use%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2FChorus.ai%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EChorus%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20detects%20conversion%20drop-off%20points.%20For%20example%2C%20our%20salesperson%20spent%20too%20long%20discussing%20deliverables%20on%20the%20call.%20When%20we%20removed%20that%20section%2C%20our%20sales%20went%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2FChorus.ai%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EChorus%3C%2Fa%3E%20also%20helped%20us%20identify%20bonuses%20for%20our%20packages.%20The%20tool%20tracks%20patterns%20and%20key%20phrases%20in%20customer%20calls%20and%20helped%20us%20realize%20that%20people%20wanted%20prompts%2C%20so%20we%20include%20those%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe've%20made%20over%20%242%20million%20in%202023%20by%20helping%20people%20understand%20AI%20largely%20because%20of%20AI%20tools%20we've%20implemented%20in%20our%20own%20business%20that%20ensure%20nothing%20slips%20through%20the%20cracks.%20Every%20person%20gets%20spoken%20with%20and%20followed%20up%20with%2C%20which%20is%20critical%20to%20the%20growth%20of%20our%20business.%20Marketing%20without%20sales%20is%20useless%2C%20and%20now%20we%20can%20do%20it%20for%20much%20cheaper%20with%20AI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-sell-ai-products-made-millions-2023-9%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693910484000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64f07bc5491bf00019b2cdd5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-sell-ai-products-made-millions-2023-9%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Chris%20Winfield%20started%20selling%20AI%20courses%20as%20part%20of%20his%20brand%20coaching%20business%20as%20well%20as%20using%20AI%20daily%20in%20his%20business%20to%20boost%20revenue.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Ashley%20Couto)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-sell-ai-products-made-millions-2023-9%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Elon%20Musk%20called%20Burning%20Man%20the%20'best%20art%20on%20Earth'%20before%20thousands%20of%20mud-soaked%20attendees%20fled%20the%20disastrous%20event%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221018%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22People%20wade%20through%20mud%20at%20Burning%20Man%202023.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64f4c9da1b7ced0019c7959e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22723%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EPeople%20wade%20through%20mud%20and%20water%20at%20Burning%20Man.%3Cp%3EJULIE%20JAMMOT%2FGetty%20Images%3C