%20a%20folder.%20I%20saw%20this%20Airbnb%20with%20views%20of%20the%20Great%20Pyramid%20of%20Giza.%20In%20the%20video%2C%20the%20guy%20is%20in%20bed%20and%20the%20woman%20is%20in%20this%20tub.%20The%20window%20shades%20start%20to%20come%20up%20and%20the%20pyramids%20come%20into%20view.%20I%20was%20like%2C%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20amazing!%26quot%3B%20They%20made%20it%20look%20really%2C%20really%20good.%20They%20made%20it%20look%20super%20sexy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20friend%20of%20mine%20runs%20a%20group%20for%20travelers%20of%20color%20called%20NoMadness%20Travel%20Tribe.%20I've%20been%20a%20member%20for%2010%20years%20or%20so%20and%20they%20were%20running%20a%20group%20trip%20to%20Egypt%20this%20past%20February.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20when%20I%20found%20out%20that%20I%20was%20going%20to%20Egypt%2C%20I%20went%20back%20to%20my%20folder%20and%20was%20like%2C%20%26quot%3BOh%2C%20let%20me%20go%20check%20this%20Airbnb%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20it%20was%20available.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20thought%20I%20was%20prepared%2C%20but%20finding%20the%20Airbnb%20was%20a%20hassle%20and%20the%20building%20was%20even%20older%20than%20I%20expected%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20read%20the%20reviews%20that%20warned%20me%20about%20the%20exterior%20and%20said%20it%20was%20tough%20to%20find.%20It%20was%20a%20lot%20more%20difficult%20to%20find%20than%20I%20thought.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20first%20got%20there%2C%20my%20Uber%20driver%20didn't%20speak%20English.%20We%20were%20trying%20to%20communicate%20to%20figure%20out%20where%20this%20place%20was.%20And%20then%20someone%20on%20the%20street%20stopped%20to%20try%20and%20help.%20Then%2C%20a%20bunch%20of%20guys%20came%20over.%20At%20one%20point%2C%20I'm%20surrounded%20by%20five%20men.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'll%20be%20perfectly%20honest%2C%20there%20was%20a%20moment%20of%20panic%20because%20I'm%20a%20woman%20by%20myself%20in%20a%20foreign%20country.%20But%20I%20tend%20to%20believe%20there%20are%20more%20good%20people%20than%20bad%20in%20the%20world.%20And%20I%20genuinely%20felt%20like%20they%20were%20trying%20to%20help%20me.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22raw%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Cblockquote%20cite%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tiktok.com%2F%40libryiajones%2Fvideo%2F7258007384738516267%5C%22%20data-video-id%3D%5C%227258007384738516267%5C%22%3E%20%3Csection%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tiktok.com%2F%40libryiajones%3Frefer%3Dembed%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22%40libryiajones%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%40libryiajones%3C%2Fa%3E%20Solely%20based%20on%20the%20exterior%E2%80%A6I%20would%E2%80%99ve%20gotten%20back%20into%20my%20Uber%20and%20went%20back%20to%20the%20Le%20Merid%C3%ADen%20%F0%9F%98%82%F0%9F%98%82%20This%20is%20a%20popular%20AirBnB%20on%20the%20TikTok%E2%80%99s%20and%20IGs%20bc%20of%20these%20very%20special%20views%20and%20this%20random%20hot%20tub.%20I%20didn%E2%80%99t%20use%20the%20hot%20tub%20but%20the%20view%20of%20the%20pyramids%20was%20%F0%9F%A4%8C%F0%9F%8F%BE%20The%20doorman%20was%20actually%20super%20nice.%20I%E2%80%99ve%20never%20used%20TikTok%20stories%20but%20I%E2%80%99ll%20share%20more%20views%20of%20this%20cute%20little%20spot%20as%20well%20as%20a%20link%20in%20my%20stories%20OR%20head%20over%20to%20my%20IG%20it%E2%80%99s%20in%20my%20highlights%20(my%20name%20is%20the%20same%20over%20there)%20Quick%20tip%20tho%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20very%20difficult%20to%20find.%20Like%20I%E2%80%99m%20thinking%20about%20doing%20a%20blog%20post%20on%20it%20and%20including%20the%20directions%20(I%20took%20photos%20of%20the%20surrounding%20streets).%20If%20you%E2%80%99re%20landing%20late%20at%20night%20don%E2%80%99t%20make%20this%20the%20first%20place%20you%E2%80%99re%20staying.%20A%20lot%20of%20flight%20land%20around%20midnight%20and%20I%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20imagine%20being%20lost%20around%20here%20at%201am.%20Ok%20back%20to%20this%20view!!!!%20%F0%9F%98%8D%F0%9F%98%8D%40Travel%20Noire%20%40Blacktravelfeed%20%40airbnb%20%40Airbnb%20Finds%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tiktok.com%2Fmusic%2FPharaoh-6891721823587665921%3Frefer%3Dembed%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22%E2%99%AC%20Pharaoh%20-%20Farooc%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%E2%99%AC%20Pharaoh%20-%20Farooc%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3C%2Fsection%3E%20%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20they%20were.%20One%20of%20the%20guys%20recognized%20the%20pictures%20and%20said%20there%20was%20a%20popular%20Airbnb%20just%20down%20a%20side%20street.%20It%20was%20all%20just%20a%20bit%20disorienting%20when%20you%20land%20in%20a%20country%20where%20you%20don't%20speak%20the%20language%20and%20it's%20not%20a%20touristy%20area.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20outside%20of%20the%20building%20didn't%20necessarily%20match%20the%20inside%2C%20but%20I%20knew%20that%20going%20in.%20One%20thing%20that%20you'll%20find%20on%20Airbnb%20is%20a%20lot%20of%20times%2C%20people%20don't%20post%20photos%20of%20the%20exterior%20or%20the%20surrounding%20areas.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20will%20say%2C%20I%20was%20still%20a%20little%20shocked%20when%20I%20got%20there.%20The%20building%20was%20a%20lot%20older%20than%20I%20thought%20it%20was%20going%20to%20be.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20elevator%20was%20such%20a%20paradox.%20On%20the%20one%20side%2C%20it%20was%20very%20old-world%20charm%20and%20beautiful.%20And%20on%20the%20other%20side%2C%20it%20was%20like%2C%20%26quot%3BIs%20this%20up%20to%20code%3F%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThere%20is%20no%20feeling%20like%20seeing%20the%20pyramids%20in%20person%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20views%20made%20it%20all%20worth%20it.%20When%20I%20walked%20in%2C%20that%20was%20my%20first%20time%20seeing%20the%20pyramids%20in%20real%20life.%20I%20saw%20them%20in%20full%20for%20the%20first%20time%20ever%20in%20this%20room.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20way%20to%20the%20Airbnb%2C%20you%20don't%20pass%20by%20them%20in%20full%20view%20or%20anything.%20I%20could%20only%20see%20the%20tops%20from%20the%20car.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYou've%20seen%20them%20on%20television%20and%20social%20media%20before.%20They're%20in%20movies%2C%20they're%20in%20pictures.%20You've%20%26quot%3Bseen%26quot%3B%20the%20pyramids.%20But%2C%20in%20person%2C%20it%20was%20just%20completely%20breathtaking.%20My%20photos%20cannot%20even%20do%20it%20justice.%20It's%20not%20even%20about%20the%20view%20itself%2C%20it's%20about%20the%20experience%20of%20seeing%20them.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22886%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20woman%20walks%20in%20front%20of%20the%20GReat%20Pyramids%20of%20Giza.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64f23a967819260019102328%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22591%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EJones%20in%20front%20of%20the%20pyramids.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Libryia%20Jones%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20plan%20was%20to%20just%20stay%20for%20one%20night%2C%20but%20I%20actually%20booked%20my%20hotel%20for%20longer%20than%20I%20was%20supposed%20to.%20It%20was%20too%20late%20to%20cancel%20the%20Airbnb%20and%20the%20hotel%20was%20nicer%2C%20so%20I%20ended%20up%20just%20spending%20the%20day%20there.%20I%20hung%20out%2C%20lounged%20around%2C%20had%20some%20coffee%2C%20and%20talked%20to%20the%20doorman.%20He%20had%20a%20friend%20who%20ended%20up%20showing%20me%20around.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20guys%20are%20very%20enterprising.%20They%20know%20that%20there's%20a%20popular%20Airbnb%2C%20so%20they'll%20hang%20out%20and%20make%20conversation.%20He%20offered%20me%20a%20day%20rate%20to%20take%20me%20around%20Cairo%2C%20which%20I%20declined.%20After%20our%20day%2C%20though%2C%20I%20did%20tip%20him%20afterwards.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20thought%20the%20stay%20was%20worth%20it%2C%20but%20it%20might%20not%20be%20for%20everyone%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20think%20for%20some%20people%2C%20it%20wouldn't%20be%20worth%20it.%20The%20views%20are%20great%2C%20but%20there's%20really%20nice%20hotels%20near%20the%20pyramids%2C%20too.%20There's%20even%20a%20Pizza%20Hut%20where%20you%20can%20get%20good%20views%20of%20the%20pyramids.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20me%2C%20it%20was%20worth%20it.%20It%20was%20a%20really%20good%20value.%20One%20night%20was%20%2483.%20It%20was%20nestled%20in%20this%20community%20where%20I%20could%20get%20away%20from%20touristy%20Cairo.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22627%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Jones%20at%20a%20colorful%20outdoor%20market%20in%20Egypt%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64f22d851b7ced0019c6ed0c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22471%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EJones%20loved%20discovering%20the%20neighborhood%20near%20her%20Airbnb.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Libryia%20Jones%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20food%20that%20I%20had%20around%20the%20corner%20from%20the%20Airbnb%20was%20some%20of%20the%20best%20food%20I've%20had%20my%20entire%20trip.%20Chicken%20kebab%2C%20rice%2C%20baba%20ghanoush%2C%20hummus%20%E2%80%94%20the%20whole%20meal%20was%20just%20%2413.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20always%20read%20the%20reviews%20of%20a%20viral%20Airbnb%20beforehand%20and%20I%20usually%20don't%20book%20an%20Airbnb%20for%20the%20very%20first%20night%20of%20a%20trip%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EJust%20keep%20in%20mind%2C%20when%20people%20are%20sharing%20these%20viral%20Airbnbs%2C%20there's%20quite%20a%20bit%20they're%20not%20showing%20you.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20tub%20I%20originally%20saw%20ended%20up%20being%20very%20weird.%20The%20video%20that%20I%20saw%20on%20Instagram%20made%20it%20look%20all%20sexy.%20It%20was%20kind%20of%20a%20hot%20tub%2Fsauna%20situation%2C%20but%20it%20was%20literally%20right%20next%20to%20the%20bed.%20It%20was%20very%20strange.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22627%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Jones%20poses%20in%20front%20of%20an%20Egyptian%20statue%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64f22dc81b7ced0019c6ed78%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22470%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EJones%20said%20travelers%20need%20to%20do%20their%20research%20before%20booking%20viral%20Airbnbs.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Libryia%20Jones%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%C2%A0%C2%A0%3Cp%3EWhen%20booking%20these%20viral%20spots%2C%20you%20need%20to%20read%20the%20reviews.%20People%20pointed%20out%20that%20it%20was%20tough%20to%20find%20and%20someone%20specifically%20said%20they%20had%20landed%20late%20at%20night%2C%20like%20I%20did.%20If%20I%20hadn't%20read%20beforehand%2C%20I%20would%20have%20been%20really%20uncomfortable%20getting%20there%20at%20midnight.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20general%2C%20I%20try%20not%20to%20book%20an%20Airbnb%20the%20first%20night%20if%20I'm%20flying%20in%20late.%20You%20can't%20predict%20how%20difficult%20it's%20going%20to%20be%20to%20find.%20Whenever%20I%20fly%2C%20if%20I'm%20going%20to%20land%20after%208%20p.m.%20or%209%20p.m.%2C%20I'm%20just%20going%20to%20book%20a%20hotel%20that's%20easy%20to%20find.%20Keep%20it%20safe.%20Then%20I'll%20go%20to%20an%20Airbnb%20the%20next%20day%20in%20the%20daylight.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Freview-of-viral-airbnb-overlooking-the-great-pyramid-of-giza-2023-9%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693907401000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64f23b5e7819260019102506%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Freview-of-viral-airbnb-overlooking-the-great-pyramid-of-giza-2023-9%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Content%20creator%20Libryia%20Jones%20rented%20an%20Airbnb%20in%20Giza%2C%20Egypt%2C%20she%20saw%20on%20social%20media.%20She%20said%20it's%20crucial%20to%20read%20the%20reviews