r%20name%20from%20UPA%20to%20INDIA%20to%20hide%20how%20they%20schemed%20against%20the%20poor...%20The%20name%20INDIA%20is%20not%20to%20show%20their%20patriotism%20but%20with%20an%20intention%20to%20rob%20the%20country%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENot%20just%20politicians%20reacted%20to%20the%20%26quot%3BBharat%26quot%3B%20move.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22hi%5C%22%3ET%204759%20-%20%F0%9F%87%AE%F0%9F%87%B3%20%E0%A4%AD%E0%A4%BE%E0%A4%B0%E0%A4%A4%20%E0%A4%AE%E0%A4%BE%E0%A4%A4%E0%A4%BE%20%E0%A4%95%E0%A5%80%20%E0%A4%9C%E0%A4%AF%20%F0%9F%9A%A9%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Amitabh%20Bachchan%20(%40SrBachchan)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSrBachchan%2Fstatus%2F1698964894383825216%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3ESeptember%205%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmitabh%20Bachchan%20kept%20his%20tweet%20short.%20%26quot%3BBharat%20Mata%20ki%20Jai%2C%26quot%3B%20wrote%20the%20megastar.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693905600000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-02%2F5jigm1ko_g20-summit_625x300_21_February_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpresident-draupadi-murmus-g20-dinner-invite-sparks-buzz-republic-of-bharat-4360671%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20term%20%26quot%3BPresident%20of%20Bharat%26quot%3B%20has%20been%20used%20for%20the%20first%20time%20in%20an%20official%20invite%20to%20foreign%20leaders%20attending%20the%20weekend%20G20%20summit%2C%20replacing%20the%20traditional%20%26quot%3BPresident%20of%20India%26quot%3B.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpresident-draupadi-murmus-g20-dinner-invite-sparks-buzz-republic-of-bharat-4360671%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpresident-draupadi-murmus-g20-dinner-invite-sparks-buzz-