0to%20something%20else.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20gave%20me%20clarity%2C%20because%20I%20knew%20that%20when%20someone%20was%20calling%2C%20it%20wasn't%20going%20to%20be%20for%20an%20emergency%20%E2%80%94%20because%20she%20was%20handling%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20also%20assigned%20work%20to%20my%20team%20that%20matched%20their%20personal%20motivations%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EHappy%20people%20are%20more%20productive%20and%20it%20meant%20less%20emotional%20burden%20for%20me%20to%20carry.%20One%20employee%20wanted%20to%20be%20seen%20as%20the%20senior%20expert%20in%20his%20field%2C%20so%20I%20gave%20him%20and%20a%20new%20hire%20a%20project%20to%20work%20on%20together.%20This%20helped%20me%20train%20my%20new%20hire%20and%20also%20motivated%20my%20senior%20employee.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20time%2C%20I%20had%20an%20associate%20who%20loved%20operations%20and%20execution%20and%20hated%20ambiguity.%20So%20I%20gave%20them%20quick%20wins%20like%20database%20management%20and%20clean-up%20that%20was%20easy%20for%20them.%20This%20not%20only%20helped%20them%20feel%20less%20overwhelmed%2C%20but%20also%20helped%20me%20on%20a%20task%20that%20would've%20probably%20been%20ignored%20until%20something%20broke.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EMy%20quiet%20quitting%20plan%20helped%20me%20plan%20my%20wedding%2C%20attend%20bachelorettes%2C%20go%20on%20my%20honeymoon%2C%20and%20attend%20a%20handful%20of%20other%20family%20events%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20daily%20routine%20became%20clearer%20and%20I%20regained%20control%20over%20my%20schedule.%20I%20created%20better%20boundaries%20and%20signed%20off%20every%20day%20around%206%20p.m.%20to%20focus%20on%20my%20wedding.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETwo%20months%20into%20my%20quiet%20quitting%20timeline%2C%20I%20went%20to%20Italy%20on%20a%20two-week%20family%20vacation.%20I%20set%20this%20up%20as%20the%20first%20%26quot%3Btest%26quot%3B%20for%20my%20successor%20to%20run%20the%20team%20without%20me.%20We%20planned%20a%20post-mortem%20to%20review%20what%20she%20did%20when%20I%20got%20back.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFour%20months%20into%20my%20plan%2C%20I%20went%20on%20two%20bachelorettes%2C%20got%20married%2C%20and%20went%20on%20my%20honeymoon.%20I%20was%20no%20longer%20in%20%26quot%3Btest%26quot%3B%20mode%20with%20my%20successor%20%E2%80%94%20we%20were%20in%20full%20operation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20this%20groundwork%20done%2C%20the%20rest%20of%20year%20was%20smooth%20sailing.%20I%20even%20had%20to%20request%20an%20exception%20to%20go%20five%20days%20over%20my%20year's%20PTO%20allotment%2C%20taking%20a%20total%20of%2035%20days%20in%202022.%20And%20during%20my%20PTO%2C%20I%20only%20ever%20had%20to%20answer%20one%20or%20two%20minor%20text%20messages.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EAs%20my%20team%20became%20more%20self-sufficient%20and%20motivated%2C%20I%20realized%20I'd%20eliminated%20my%20own%20position%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20meant%20it%20was%20time%20for%20me%20to%20leave.%20In%20March%202023%2C%20I%20left%20my%20company%2C%20and%20it%20felt%20like%20a%20satisfying%20relief.%20My%20mission%20was%20accomplished%2C%20and%20I%20think%20I%20left%20the%20company%20in%20a%20better%20place.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhat%20I%20found%20during%20my%20eight%20months%20of%20quiet%20quitting%20is%20that%20it's%20easy%20to%20fall%20into%20a%20passive%20state%20and%20stay%20there.%20Maintaining%20boundaries%2C%20managing%20well%2C%20motivating%20others%2C%20and%20shaping%20your%20own%20life%20at%20work%20and%20at%20home%20takes%20discipline%2C%20dedication%2C%20and%20a%20good%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ELooking%20back%2C%20I%20can't%20believe%20I%20was%20living%20the%20way%20I%20was%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20burnt%20out%2C%20constantly%20on%20calls%2C%20fielding%20problems%2C%20and%20had%20little%20to%20no%20personal%20time.%20I%20worked%20long%20hours%20and%20after%20work%2C%20I%20had%20to%20handle%20household%20duties%20and%20plan%20a%20wedding%20with%20almost%20no%20headspace%20to%20th