nsferrable%20skills%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20like%20analytical%20expertise%20and%20time%20management%2C%20looked%20for%20jobs%20with%20those%20skills%20listed%20on%20LinkedIn%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2FGovernmentJobs.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGovernmentJobs.com%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20made%20sure%20my%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9%20highlighted%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20also%20selective%20with%20the%20roles%20I%20applied%20to%2C%20because%20a%20job%20search%20is%20a%20job%20in%20itself%2C%20so%20I%20didn't%20apply%20to%20jobs%20that%20were%20too%20far%20below%20what%20I%20wanted.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EMy%20next%20job%20came%20with%20a%20raise%20to%20%2469%2C500%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20pivoted%20to%20the%20LA%20County%20Library%20as%20a%20management%20fellow%20in%20May%202018%2C%20it%20was%20a%20scary%20jump%2C%20and%20I%20wasn't%20sure%20I%20was%20ready%20or%20qualified.%20But%20I%20went%20for%20it%20anyway%20and%20received%20my%20first%20big%20pay%20bump%2C%20to%20%2469%2C500.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20always%20looking%20for%20the%20next%20step%20in%20my%20career%2C%20and%20you%20should%2C%20too.%20Switching%20jobs%20can%20be%20a%20top%20method%20for%20earning%20a%20higher%20salary.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you're%20not%20receiving%20an%20annual%20raise%20of%203%20to%205%25%2C%20look%20for%20a%20bigger%20role%20in%20the%20same%20company%2C%20a%20similar%20role%20in%20a%20new%20company%2C%20or%20even%20a%20new%20job%20in%20a%20new%20industry.%20You%20should%20be%20constantly%20evaluating%20your%20needs%20and%20wants%2C%20and%20what%20is%2C%20or%20isn't%2C%20working%20in%20your%20current%20job.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20driver%20for%20me%20is%20looking%20beyond%20the%20salary%2C%20which%20is%20still%20important%20because%20I%20want%20to%20retire%20early.%20But%20I%20also%20want%20job%20stability%2C%20growth%2C%20benefits%2C%20and%20a%20solid%20organization%2C%20especially%20as%20a%20parent%20with%20other%20responsibilities%20outside%20