id%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20haven%E2%80%99t%20invited%20her%E2%80%9D.%20He%20refused%20to%20elaborate%20on%20further%20questions%20on%20her%20joining%20the%20grouping.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Mayawati%20is%20learned%20to%20have%20categorically%20instructed%20party%20cadres%20to%20not%20vote%20or%20vote%20NOTA%20in%20the%20Ghosi%20bypolls%2C%20this%20writer%20has%20received%20reports%20that%20seem%20to%20suggest%20that%20large%20numbers%20of%20Dalit%20voters%20have%20in%20fact%20been%20arriving%20to%20vote.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20close%20look%20into%20the%20BSP%20particularly%20after%202022%20assembly%20elections%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20suggests%20that%20Mayawati%20is%20faced%20with%20the%20worst-ever%20crisis.%20Her%20party%E2%80%99s%20vote%20share%20plummeted%20to%2012.88%25%20in%202022%20from%2022.2%25%20in%20the%202017%20elections.%20It%20was%20the%20lowest%20vote%20share%20for%20the%20BSP%20in%2030%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BSP%20had%20notably%20registered%20its%20emphatic%20presence%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%E2%80%99s%20politics%20by%20joining%20hands%20with%20Mulayam%20Singh%20Yadav%E2%80%99s%20Samajwadi%20Party%20and%20defeating%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20in%20the%201993%20assembly%20polls.%20This%20had%20taken%20place%20within%20months%20of%20the%20demolition%20of%20the%20Babri%20mosque%20at%20Ayodhya%20in%20December%2C%201992.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3EMile%20Mulayam-Kanshi%20Ram%2C%20hawa%20mein%20ud%20gaya%20%E2%80%98Jai%20Shri%20Ram%E2%80%99.%E2%80%9D%20%3C%2Fem%3EThis%20was%20the%20catchy%20slogan%20of%20the%20times.%20Translated%2C%20it%20means%2C%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20Mulayam%20and%20Kanshi%20Ram%20come%20together%2C%20one%20can%20no%20longer%20hear%20%E2%80%98Jai%20Shri%20Ram%2C%E2%80%99%20Hindutva%20groups%E2%80%99%20rallying%20cry.%20Kanshi%20Ram%20was%20Mayawati%E2%80%99s%20mentor.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESP-BSP%20formed%20a%20government%20with%20Mulayam%20as%20the%20chief%20minister.%20As%20per%20the%20agreement%20between%20the%20two%20parties%2C%20the%20CM%E2%80%99s%20post%20was%20to%20be%20rotated%20between%20Mulayam%20and%20Mayawati.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fbsp-mayawati-support-caste-census%5C%22%3EBSP%20Chief%20Mayawati%20Reiterates%20Support%20for%20Caste%20Census%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20agreement%20didn%E2%80%99t%20work%20and%20the%20party%20cadres%20fought%20violently%20against%20each%20other.%20They%20parted%20ways%20over%20a%20year%20later.%20But%20by%20then%20Mayawati%20had%20emerged%20as%20the%20most%20potent%20Dalit%20leader%20in%20the%20heartland%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESubsequently%2C%20she%20became%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20chief%20minister%20four%20times%20either%20with%20the%20support%20of%20the%20BJP%20or%20the%20SP%20and%20Congress.%20In%202007%2C%20her%20BSP%20succeeded%20in%20forming%20the%20government%20on%20its%20own%2C%20winning%20206%20seats%20and%20securing%20over%2030%25%20votes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20party%20did%20well%20in%202009%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%20too%20by%20winning%2021%20seats.%20The%20BSP%E2%80%99s%20fortune%20has%20fallen%20since%202007%2C%20but%20it%20kept%20on%20polling%20about%2020%25%20to%2023%25%20votes%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20and%20assembly%20elections%20even%20after%20that.%20In%202022%2C%20for%20the%20first%20time%2C%20its%20vote%20share%20went%20down%20to%2012.88%20%25%2C%20reducing%20it%20to%20almost%20an%20irrelevant%20force%20in%20the%20heartland%E2%80%99s%20politics.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20largely%20understood%20that%20accommodating%20Brahmins%2C%20forever%20powerful%20in%20the%20caste%20dynamics%20of%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20and%20tactically%20allying%20with%20the%20SP%20and%20the%20BJP%20had%20kept%20the%20party%20alive.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20party%20won%2010%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%20in%20alliance%20with%20the%20SP%20and%20the%20Rashtriya%20Lok%20Dal%20(RLD)%20in%20the%202019%20polls.%20But%20in%20the%202014%20polls%2C%20it%20had%20won%20zero.%20Remarkably%2C%20the%20BSP%E2%80%99s%20vote%20share%20in%202014%20and%202019%20was%20almost%20same%20between%2019%25%20and%2021%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0The%20point%20is%2C%20despite%20the%20BSP%20enjoying%20the%20support%20of%20the%20Dalits%20it%20could%20not%20convert%20its%20vote%20share%20into%20seats.%20It%20can%20perform%20better%20at%20elections%20by%20harmonising%20itself%20with%20other%20parties.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FQ4XXZ-ZgT3c%3Ffeature%3Doembed%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22840%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22One%20Mayawati%20Born%20in%20a%20100%20years%2C%20the%20Story%20of%20a%20Dalit%20Daughter%20to%20Chief%20Minister%20%7C%20Uttar%20Pradesh%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22473%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMayawati%20Vs%20Ram%20Vilas%20Paswan%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20Mayawati%20was%20the%20Dalit%20leader%20of%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20then%20Ram%20Vilas%20Paswan%20was%20the%20same%20in%20Bihar.%20But%20there%20have%20been%20three%20broad%20differences%20between%20the%20politics%20of%20Mayawati%20and%20Paswan%20who%20died%20in%20October%202020.%20First%2C%20while%20he%20too%20struck%20an%20alliance%20with%20the%20BJP%20in%20accordance%20with%20situations%2C%20he%20was%20keen%20to%20never%20allow%20his%20support%20base%20to%20shift%20to%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELike%20Mayawati%20whose%20support%20base%20was%20confined%20to%20her%20Jatav%20caste%2C%20Ram%20Vilas%20also%20was%20confined%20to%20his%20Paswan%20caste%20groups%20in%20the%20later%20years%20of%20his%20long%20career.%20But%20the%20non-Paswan%20Dalits%20communities%2C%20even%20when%20they%20drifted%20from%20Paswan%2C%20went%20either%20to%20Lalu%20or%20Nitish%20Kumar%20or%20the%20CPI-ML-Liberation.%20They%20remained%20socialists%2C%20largely%2C%20and%20did%20not%20vote%20for%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThirdly%20and%20most%20importantly%2C%20Ram%20Vilas%20who%20had%20made%20records%20by%20winning%20Bihar%E2%80%99s%20Hajipur%20Lok%20Sabha%20seat%20with%20the%20highest%20margins%20twice%20in%20the%201970s%20and%2080s%20had%20a%20strong%20grip%20on%20Bihar%20politics%20but%20always%20remained%20in%20national%20politics.%20He%20fought%20and%20befriended%20Lalu%20and%20Nitish%20at%20different%20points%20of%20time%20but%20never%20eyed%20the%20Bihar%20chief%20minister%E2%80%99s%20post.%20He%20was%20smarter%20than%20that%20and%20remained%20minister%20under%20all%20the%20prime%20ministers%20from%20Vishwanath%20Pratap%20Singh%20in%201989%20to%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20till%20he%20died%20in%202020.%20He%20was%20better%20than%20Mayawati%20in%20judging%20his%20own%20limitations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBipolar%20politics%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJudging%20by%20the%20indications%20available%2C%20as%20of%20now%2C%20north%20India%20is%20all%20set%20to%20witness%20bipolar%20politics%20between%20INDIA%20and%20NDA%20in%20the%20run%20up%20to%20the%202024%20elections.%20The%20BJP%20has%2C%20apparently%2C%20been%20using%20the%20BSP%20as%20the%20%E2%80%98third%20party%E2%80%99%20to%20make%20the%20battle%20in%20UP%20triangular.%20The%20BJP%20has%20always%20done%20well%20in%20multi-cornered%20contests.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20observers%20of%20north%20India%E2%80%99s%20politics%20believe%20that%20in%20the%20months%20to%20follow%2C%20the%20BSP%20will%20be%20marginalised%20further%20as%20the%20scope%20of%20a%20third%20party%20will%20shrink%20in%20the%20battle%20between%20INDIA%20and%20NDA.%20The%20BSP%E2%80%99s%20Balmiki%20and%20other%20non-Jatav%20community%20support%20base%20is%20said%20to%20have%20largely%20shifted%20to%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENitish%20Kumar%2C%20who%20has%20worked%20closely%20with%20Akhilesh%20Yadav%20to%20rope%20in%20the%20Dalit%20votes%20for%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%2C%20is%20understood%20have%20not%20made%20any%20attempts%20to%20involve%20Mayawati.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%