%20meeting%20with%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20US%20President%20Joe%20Biden%20and%20other%20world%20leaders%20by%20cancelling%20his%20scheduled%20appearance%20at%20the%20two-day%20G20%20summit%20in%20Delhi%20starting%20September%209.%20He%20has%20now%20asked%20his%20Ministry%20of%20Security%20to%20find%20reasons%20that%20would%20allow%20him%20to%20skip%20the%20next%20major%20international%20meet%20in%20November.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Chinese%20foreign%20ministry%20has%20said%20Premier%20Li%20Qiang%20will%20attend%20the%20G20%20while%20suggesting%20that%20Xi%20will%20skip%20it.%20Li%20was%20earlier%20the%20Communist%20Party%20chief%20for%20Shanghai%20city%20but%20he%20has%20very%20little%20experience%20in%20the%20diplomatic%20field.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPremier%20Li%20Qiang%20will%20elaborate%20on%20China's%20views%20and%20propositions%20on%20G20%20cooperation%2C%20promote%20the%20G20%20to%20strengthen%20solidarity%20and%20cooperation%20and%20work%20together%20to%20address%20global%20economic%20and%20development%20challenges%2C%26quot%3B%20Chinese%20Foreign%20Ministry%20spokesperson%20Mao%20Ning%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChina%20is%20ready%20to%20work%20with%20all%20parties%20%26quot%3Bto%20jointly%20promote%20the%20success%20of%20the%20G20%26quot%3B%20summit%20and%20%26quot%3Bmake%20positive%20contributions%20to%20promoting%20the%20stable%20recovery%20of%20the%20world%20economy%20and%20promoting%20sustainable%20development%2C%26quot%3B%20Mao%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%2C%20analysts%20say%20Premier%20Li%20will%20be%20directed%20by%20Xi%20sitting%20in%20Beijing%20and%20will%20likely%20take%20no%20initiatives%20on%20his%20own.%20As%20with%20most%20Chinese%20leaders%2C%20he%20will%20try%20not%20to%20raise%20his%20international%20profile%20because%20Xi%20may%20not%20like%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ELooking%20for%20excuses%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20another%20level%2C%20China's%20Ministry%20of%20Security%20has%20indicated%20that%20Xi%20may%20not%20attend%20another%20important%20international%20meeting%20-%20the%20Asia%20Pacific%20Leaders'%20meet%20at%20San%20Francisco%20in%20November.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20statement%2C%20China's%20Ministry%20of%20Security%20found%20fault%20with%20Washington's%20%26quot%3Btwo-faced%26quot%3B%20China%20policy.%20%26quot%3BTo%20truly%20realise%20the%20move%20from%20Bali%20to%20San%20Francisco%2C%20the%20US%20needs%20to%20show%20real%20sincerity%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%20Bali%20is%20where%20the%20last%20G20%20meeting%20took%20place%2C%20and%20San%20Francisco%20is%20the%20site%20of%20the%20upcoming%20conclave%20of%20Asia%20Pacific%20leaders.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ministry%20said%20the%20US%20has%20taken%20several%20steps%20to%20undermine%20China%20as%20it%20%26quot%3Bdownplayed%20China's%20economy%26quot%3B%20and%20approved%20arms%20sales%20and%20military%20assistance%20to%20Taiwan.%20China%20regards%20Taiwan%20as%20part%20of%20its%20territory%20and%20opposes%20American%20efforts%20to%20arm%20the%20island.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20complaining%20against%20the%20US%2C%20China%20is%20preparing%20grounds%20for%20Xi%20Jinping%20to%20skip%20the%20meeting%20in%20San%20Francisco%2C%20which%20will%20be%20attended%20by%20several%20world%20leaders%20including%20President%20Biden.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBiden%2C%20who%20is%20expected%20to%20discuss%20weighty%20international%20issues%20with%20the%20Chinese%20leader%2C%20said%20he%20was%20disappointed%20by%20Xi's%20decision%20to%20stay%20away.%20But%2C%20he%20is%20still%20hoping%20Xi%20will%20attend%20the%20meeting%20in%20San%20Francisco.%20%26quot%3BI%20am%20disappointed%2C%20but%20I%20am%20going%20to%20get%20to%20see%20him%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhy%20is%20Xi%20passing%20up%20the%20opportunity%20to%20interact%20with%20world%20leaders%2C%20which%20is%20a%20reversal%20of%20his%20policy%20of%20presenting%20himself%20as%20a%20global%20leader%20and%20peacemaker%20on%20different%20international%20forums%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Chinese%20President%20is%20clearly%20trying%20to%20avoid%20awkward%20questions%20about%20the%20state%20of%20the%20Chinese%20economy%2C%20which%20is%20a%20matter%20of%20grave%20concern%20to%20financial%20markets%20the%20world%20over.%20China's%20global%20influence%20has%20severely%20declined%20due%20to%20the%20economic%20slide%20seen%20even%20after%20the%20end%20of%20the%20Covid%20pandemic%20period%2C%20and%20bleak%20prospects%20for%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWithin%20China%2C%20the%20ruling%20Communist%20Party%20is%20reassessing%20the%20country's%20economic%20policy%20because%20foreign%20direct%20investments%20have%20fallen%20to%20the%20lowest%20level%20in%2025%20years%2C%20and%20the%20US%20is%20creating%20new%20hurdles%20in%20the%20way%20of%20Chinese%20companies%20almost%20every%20month.%20The%20party%20is%20also%20worried%20about%20internal%20turmoil%20as%20urban%20youth%20employment%20has%20fallen%20to%20the%20lowest%20level%20in%20decades.%20Put%20simply%2C%20Xi%20finds%20himself%20unable%20to%20defend%20his%20%C2%A0governance%20on%20the%20world%20stage%20at%20this%20point.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EXi%20feels%20isolated%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20absence%20of%20Russian%20President%20Vladimir%20Putin%2C%20who%20will%20not%20come%20due%20to%20his%20involvement%20in%20the%20Ukraine%20war%2C%20is%20possibly%20the%20other%20reason%20he%20does%20not%20want%20to%20show%20up.%20Xi%20and%20Putin%20have%20been%20working%20together%2C%20co-ordinating%20their%20responses%20to%20global%20issues%2C%20in%20most%20international%20events%20in%20recent%20years.%20The%20absence%20of%20Putin%20makes%20Xi%20vulnerable%20to%20being%20cornered%20by%20Western%20countries%20on%20a%20range%20of%20issues%20including%20Ukraine%20and%20the%20Taiwan%20situation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20is%20more%2C%20China%20has%20few%20friends%20in%20the%20G20%20barring%20Saudi%20Arabia%2C%20Argentina%20and%20Turkey.%20Even%20these%20countries%20are%20unlikely%20to%20stand%20by%20China%20if%20they%20face%20pressures%20from%20the%20US%20in%20an%20international%20forum.%20Most%20of%20China's%20close%20partners%20are%20underdeveloped%20countries%20-which%20are%20not%20part%20of%20G20--that%20need%20Chinese%20financing%20for%20infrastructure%20projects%20and%20other%20reasons.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChina%20recently%20witnessed%20a%20serious%20military%20challenge%20as%20the%20Philippines%20joined%20Australia%20in%20conducting%20a%20naval%20exercise%20in%20the%20South%20China%20Sea.%20The%20exercise%2C%20conducted%20with%20US%20support%2C%20was%20a%20direct%20challenge%20to%20China%2C%20which%20regards%20most%20of%20the%20sea%20area%20as%20its%20own%20territory.%20The%20Chinese%20navy%20has%20often%20chased%20away%20the%20Philippines%20naval%20vessels%20from%20the%20area.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAttending%20the%20G20%20would%20amount%20to%20endorsing%20India's%20leadership%20position.%20The%20Narendra%20Modi%20government%20has%20taken%20several%20diplomatic%20initiatives%20including%20the%20move%20to%20make%20the%20African%20Union%2C%20which%20has%2051%20member%20countries%2C%20as%20a%20member%20of%20G20.%20India's%20influence%20has%20also%20grown%20due%20to%20its%20economic%20rise%2C%20its%20emergence%20as%20the%20world's%20most%20populated%20country%20and%20the%20successful%20launch%20of%20Chandrayan%20on%20the%20moon's%20surface.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEndorsing%20India's%20leadership%20role%20is%20something%20Xi%20would%20not%20want%20to%20do%20as%20China%20continues%20to%20create%20trouble%20for%20India%20on%20the%20borders%2C%20and%20stonewall%20efforts%20to%20settle%20the%20border%20dispute.%20The%20two%20countries%20recently%20expelled%20each%20other's%20journalists.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBiden%20backs%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20has%20been%20keen%20to%20encourage%20India%20to%20take%20more%20leadership%20roles%20in%20a%20manner%20that%20acts%20as%20a%20counterweight%20to%20China's%20influence%20in%20the%20world.%20Xi%20is%20in%20no%20mood%20to%20endorse%20such%20a%20situation%20with%20his%20presence%20in%20New%20Delhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPresident%20Biden%20is%20visiting%20New%20Delhi%20for%20bilateral%20talks%20with%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%20as%20a%20means%20to%20boost%20India's%20position%20on%20September%207%2C%20two%20days%20before%20the%20G20%20begins%20on%20September%209.%20The%20announcement%20is%20significant%20because%20it%20came%20soon%20after%20the%20Chinese%20foreign%20ministry%20confirmed%20that%20Xi%20would%20not%20be%20visiting%20New%20Delhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChina%20has%20blocked%20several%20proposals%20that%20India%20has%20made%20in%20different%20sectoral%20meetings%20like%20tourism%20and%20climate%20change%20connected%20with%20the%20G20.%20Beijing's%20goal%20is%20to%20block%20the%20possibility%20of%20a%20joint%20communique%20at%20the%20end%20of%20the%20meeting%20to%20stop%20India%20from%20claiming%20success.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20coming%20to%20New%20Delhi%20ahead%20of%20schedule%2C%20Biden%20is%20trying%20to%20pull%20his%20weight%20for%20India%20and%20make%20the%20G20%20a%20reasonable%20success.%20However%2C%20the%20US%20and%20other%20Western%20countries%20are%20unlikely%20to%20push%20through%20a%20resolution%20on%20Ukraine%20because%20representatives%20from%20China%20and%20Russia%20would%20oppose%20it%20tooth%20and%20nail.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Saibal%20Dasgupta%20is%20a%20journalist%2C%20author%20and%20China%20expert)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693902660000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2F865t1f7_xi-jinping-reuters_625x300_18_August_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Flooking-for-excuses-xi-skips-g20-to-avoid-tough-questions-on-economy-