2Fnews%2Fimran-khan-talks-about-old-wounds-and-scars-in-moving-new-post-netizens-pour-love-read-inside%2Farticleshow%2F103385965.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Airport%20Inefficiency%20as%20a%20Microcosm%2C%20or%20When%20Tech%20Can't%20Fix%20Everything%26nbsp%3B%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F05133227%2F1357760354_0a0fb61711_o.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EImagine%20the%20following.%20Children%20yelling.%20Mothers%20shouting%20instructions%20across%20the%20gender%20lines.%20A%20lone%20woman%20in%20her%20business%20suit%20with%20AirPods%20in%20her%20ears%20completely%20unperturbed%20by%20the%20cacophony%20while%20the%20group%20in%20front%20of%20her%20enquires%20what%20needs%20to%20be%20pulled%20out.%20Three%20men%20with%20their%20hair%20slicked%20back%20edge%20towards%20the%20crowd%20then%20look%20surprised%20when%20informed%20that%20there%20is%20in%20fact%20a%20line.%20Apparently%20they%20have%20a%20condition%20where%20they%20can%E2%80%99t%20see%20anyone%20else%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhere%20does%20this%20systematic%20chaos%20play%20out%20every%20day%3F%20It%E2%80%99s%20in%20the%20airport%20final%20security%20check%20across%20multiple%20metropolitan%20cities%20in%20India%20%E2%80%93%20a%20cartoon%20strip%20waiting%20to%20be%20drawn%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYou%20could%20try%20and%20appeal%20to%20security%20for%20order%20but%20you%20will%20be%20severely%20disappointed.%20They%20are%20only%20interested%20in%20the%20nail%20cutter%20you%20accidentally%20packed%20in%20the%20deepest%20crevice%20of%20your%20baggage.%20You%E2%80%99re%20obviously%20going%20to%20retrieve%20it%20to%20kill%20someone%20on%20the%20plane.%20Meanwhile%2C%20passengers%20scramble%20for%20trays%20from%20underneath%20the%20new%20x-ray%20machines%20with%20automatic%20tray%20return%20as%20if%20it%E2%80%99s%20a%20pile%20of%20gold%20left%20unattended.%20They%20then%20rush%20with%20the%20trays%20to%20an%20artificially%20formed%20%E2%80%9Cline%E2%80%9D%20that%20has%20little%20connection%20to%20how%20the%20new%20machines%20are%20designed.%20Passengers%20then%20argue%20about%20who%20actually%20came%20first%20and%20battle%20over%20the%20order%20of%20dumping%20loaded%20trays%20on%20the%20conveyor%20belt.%20The%20purpose%20with%20which%20this%20new%20technology%20was%20set%20up%20stands%20little%20chance%20against%20human%20ingenuity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGood%20luck%20trying%20to%20get%20security%E2%80%99s%20attention%3B%20for%20the%20most%20part%2C%20they%20are%20in%20a%20stupor%20that%20only%20their%20next%20chai%20break%20can%20shake%20them%20out%20of.%C2%A0%20They%20would%20rather%20not%20deal%20with%20all%20the%20Indians%20who%20they%20often%20blame%20for%20the%20loss%20of%20civilisation%20and%20general%20havoc%20at%20airports.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20happens%20like%20this%20because%20it%E2%80%99s%20India%2C%E2%80%9D%20we%E2%80%99ve%20been%20informed%20by%20security%20on%20more%20than%20one%20occasion.%20%E2%80%9CNo%20one%20listens.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20that%E2%80%99s%20why%20we%20just%20shut%20down%20cities%20in%20preparation%20for%20G20.%20The%20number%20of%20flights%20will%20be%20lower%20and%20thus%20the%20underlying%20problem%20can%20just%20be%20swept%20under%20the%20rug%20%E2%80%93%20along%20with%20the%20homeless%20and%20the%20strays%20%E2%80%93%20while%20the%20G20%20delegates%20enter%20and%20marvel%20at%20the%20magnificent%20infrastructure%20the%20capital%20of%20the%20largest%20democracy%20in%20the%20world%20has%20to%20offer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20inefficiency%20in%20airport%20queues%20is%20but%20one%20example%20of%20a%20systemic%20problem.%20Having%20the%20right%20infrastructure%20and%20the%20latest%20technology%20is%20a%20necessary%20condition%20for%20development%20but%20by%20no%20means%20a%20sufficient%20one.%20The%20bar%20for%20most%20operations%20%E2%80%93%20even%20those%20logistical%20in%20nature%20%E2%80%93%20is%20significantly%20higher%20than%20this%2C%20yet%20our%20vision%20and%20efforts%20struggle%20to%20face%20up%20to%20this%20reality.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20hand%20out%20tablets%20and%20hope%20that%20the%20tech%20itself%20will%20solve%20the%20education%20crisis%20despite%20years%20of%20evidence%20that%20it%20does%20not.%20We%20create%20apps%20for%20public%20health%20purposes%2C%20like%20contact%20tracing%20during%20the%20pandemic%2C%20without%20ensuring%20that%20they%E2%80%99re%20being%20used%20widely%20and%20regularly%20enough%20to%20provide%20accurate%20information.%20We%20develop%20dashboards%20for%20government%20programmes%2C%20expecting%20nice-looking%20charts%20and%20colour%20coding%20to%20change%20the%20behaviour%20of%20those%20at%20the%20frontlines%20delivering%20services%20to%20citizens.%20At%20the%20heart%20of%20these%20challenges%20is%20the%20constant%20interaction%20of%20people%2C%20who%20may%20or%20may%20not%20have%20the%20same%20perceptions%2C%20goals%2C%20incentives%20and%20temperaments.%20Hard%20infrastructure%20and%20technology%20are%20only%20two%20among%20many%20other%20%E2%80%9Chuman%E2%80%9D%20factors%20that%20determine%20whether%20these%20interactions%20produce%20outcomes%20beneficial%20for%20individuals%20and%20for%20society%20writ%20large.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20case%20of%20airports%2C%20there%20are%20some%20straightforward%20fixes%2C%20ever%20present%20in%20other%20airports%20around%20the%20world%2C%20that%20could%20make%20the%20process%20more%20pleasant%20for%20passengers.%20Training%20staff%2C%20for%20example%2C%20on%20how%20to%20use%20the%20x-ray%20machines%20the%20way%20they%20are%20designed%20in%20order%20to%20minimise%20chaos.%20Providing%20better%20guidance%20to%20travellers%20about%20how%20to%20navigate%20the%20process%20is%20another%20easy%20win.%20In%20fact%2C%20the%20authors%20are%20happy%20to%20offer%20a%20bit%20of%20encouraging%20but%20firm%20oversight%20as%20these%20solutions%20are%20trialled%2C%20for%20a%20mere%205%25%20cut%20of%