tric-buses-4360830%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22RBI%20Refused%20Govt's%20Push%20to%20Transfer%20Rs%203%20Lakh%20Crore%20in%202018%20Ahead%20of%20General%20Election%3A%20Viral%20Acharya%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F03%2F14200518%2Fimage-840.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20Reserve%20Bank%20of%20India%20(RBI)%20refused%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20proposal%20to%20extract%20%3Cspan%3ERs%20%3C%2Fspan%3E2-3%20lakh%20crore%20from%20its%20balance%20sheet%20in%202018%20for%20pre-election%20expenditure%20ahead%20of%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%20in%20the%20following%20year%2C%20former%20central%20bank%20deputy%20governor%20Viral%20Acharya%20said%20in%20a%20new%20prelude%20to%20his%20book%2C%20%3Cem%3EQuest%20for%20Restoring%20Financial%20Stability%20in%20India.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livemint.com%2Fnews%2Findia%2Fdemand-for-2-3-tn-sparked-rbi-govt-clash-says-acharya-11693852197905.html%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EMint%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20this%20new%20prelude%20is%20in%20the%20updated%20edition%20of%20his%20book%2C%20first%20published%20in%202020.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20apparently%20had%20led%20to%20the%20differences%20between%20RBI%20and%20the%20government.%20Acharya%20had%20first%20flagged%20this%20issue%20while%20delivering%20his%20speech%20at%20the%20A.D.%20Shroff%20Memorial%20Lecture%20in%20late%202018.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CCreative%20minds%20in%20the%20bureaucracy%20and%20the%20government%E2%80%9D%20devised%20a%20plan%20to%20transfer%20substantial%20sums%20accumulated%20by%20RBI%20during%20tenure%20of%20previous%20governments%20to%20the%20current%20government%E2%80%99s%20account%2C%20he%20said%20in%20the%20prelude.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEvery%20year%2C%20the%20central%20bank%20sets%20aside%20a%20part%20of%20its%20profit%2C%20instead%20of%20distributing%20it%20all%20to%20the%20government%2C%20and%20in%20three%20years%20leading%20up%20to%20demonetisation%2C%20the%20central%20bank%20made%20record%20profit%20transfers%20to%20the%20government%2C%20Acharya%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20demonetisation%20year%2C%20the%20expense%20for%20currency%20printing%20reduced%20the%20transfers%20made%20to%20the%20Centre%2C%20resulting%20in%20%E2%80%9Cintensifying%E2%80%9D%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20demand%20ahead%20of%20the%202019%20elections%2C%20he%20said%2C%20per%20the%20newspaper.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20effectively%20an%20attempt%20to%20ensure%20back-door%20monetisation%20of%20fiscal%20deficit%20by%20the%20central%20bank%2C%20he%20said.%20%E2%80%9CWhy%20cut%20populist%20expenditures%20in%20an%20election%20year%20%E2%80%A6.%20when%20the%20central%20bank%20balance%20sheet%20can%20be%20raided%20and%20surging%20fiscal%20deficits%20essentially%20monetised%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20reason%20for%20exerting%20pressure%20on%20RBI%20was%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20failure%20to%20raise%20divestment%20revenues.%20Divestment%20shortfall%20sought%20to%20be%20met%20via%20transfers%20from%20the%20RBI%20is%20an%20annual%20ritual%20now%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20RBI%20did%20not%20comply%20with%20the%20requests%20for%20the%20transfers%20sought%2C%20a%20proposal%20within%20the%20government%20suggested%20invoking%20Section%207%20of%20the%20Reserve%20Bank%20of%20India%20Act%2C%20which%20allows%20the%20government%20to%20issue%20%E2%80%98directions%20to%20the%20bank%20as%20it%20may%2C%20after%20consultation%20with%20RBI%20governor%2C%20(to%20consider%20it)%20necessary%20in%20the%20public%20interest%E2%80%99%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20invoking%20of%20this%20section%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fgovernment-to-continue-pressing-rbi-for-relaxing-norms-funds-1943860%5C%22%3Ewas%20an%20unprecedented%20move%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%2080-year%20history%20of%20RBI.%20Although%20then%20RBI%20governor%20Urjit%20Patel%20had%20cited%20personal%20reasons%20for%20resigning%20nine%20months%20before%20the%20completion%20of%20his%20three-year%20term%2C%20reports%20indicated%20the%20move%20came%20amid%20the%20central%20bank%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feconomictimes.indiatimes.com%2Findustry%2Fbanking%2Ffinance%2Fbanking%2Furjit-patel-resigns-as-the-rbi-governor%2Farticleshow%2F67026103.cms%3Ffrom%3Dmdr%5C%22%3Efacing%20pressures%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20its%20autonomy%20from%20the%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20updated%20edition%20of%20the%20book%2C%20Acharya%2C%20per%20%3Cem%3EMint%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20argued%20that%20matters%20of%20%E2%80%9Cpublic%20interest%E2%80%9D%20like%20this%20should%20be%20openly%20debated%20rather%20than%20discussed%20behind%20closed%20doors.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20notable%20example%20of%20such%20a%20transfer%20was%20the%20one%20RBI%20made%20during%20the%20pandemic%20in%202020%2C%20a%20move%20that%20was%20well%20justified%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20FY23%2C%20the%20central%20bank%20paid%20dividends%20of%20%3Cspan%3ERs%20%3C%2Fspan%3E87%2C416%20crore%20to%20the%20government.%20It%20had%20paid%20%3Cspan%3ERs%20%3C%2Fspan%3E30%2C307%20crore%20in%20FY22.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAcharya%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbanking%2Frbi-deputy-governor-viral-acharya-resigns-6-months-before-his-term-ends-report%5C%22%3Ehad%20quit%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20in%20June%202019%2C%20six%20months%20before%20his%20three-year%20term%20as%20the%20deputy%20governor%20in-charge%20of%20the%20monetary%20policy%20department.%20He%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbanking%2Fviral-acharya-rbi-deputy-governor-resignation%5C%22%3E%20had%20warned%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20any%20government%20undermining%20the%20banks%E2%80%99%20authority%20would%20face%20the%20wrath%20of%20financial%20markets%20and%20economic%20fires.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20data%20shows%20that%20governments%20tend%20to%20raise%20overall%20spending%20before%20general%20elections.%20They%20also%20often%20spend%20relatively%20more%20on%20subsidies%20and%20transfers%20ahead%20of%20polls%2C%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livemint.com%2FPolitics%2Fc2KWaGzr3uPO4UQbLSK10H%2FGovernment-spending-before-2019-Lok-Sabha-elections-What-da.html%5C%22%3E2018%20%3Cem%3EMint%20%3C%2Fem%3Ereport%20had%20said%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20cited%20historical%20data%2C%20saying%20most%20Union%20governments%20have%20resorted%20to%20fiscal%20expansion%20in%20the%20year%20ahead%20of%20general%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20Centre%20dipping%20into%20the%20coffers%20of%20the%20RBI%20to%20meet%20its%20fiscal%20deficit%20target%20has%20been%20a%20hot-button%20issue%2C%20and%20it%20has%20not%20gone%20down%20well%20with%20many%20economists%20and%20market%20players%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindubusinessline.com%2Fmoney-and-banking%2Fthe-math-behind-rbis-record-rs-176-lakh-crore-surplus-transfer-to-the-government%2Farticle29266795.ece%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EHindu%20BusinessLine%3C%2Fem%3E%20explained.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202019%2C%20RBI%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fbusiness%2Findia-business%2Frbi-board-approves-rs-1-76-lakh-crore-transfer-to-govt%2Farticleshow%2F70845849.cms%5C%22%3Ehad%20transferred%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20highest-ever%20surplus%20of%20Rs%201.76%20lakh%20crore%20to%20the%20government.%20This%20was%20in%20line%20with%20the%20recommendation%20of%20a%20committee%2C%20led%20by%20former%20RBI%20governor%20Bimal%20Jalan%2C%20that%20was%20constituted%20to%20decide%20how%20much%20capital%20reserves%20the%20central%20bank%20should%20hold.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693900648000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F03%2F14200518%2Fimage-840.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbanking%2Frbi-refused-govts-push-to-transfer-rs-3-lakh-crore-in-2018-ahead-of-general-election-viral-acharya%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22This%2C%20according%20to%20Acharya's%20updated%20edition%20of%20his%202020%20book%2C%20had%20led%20to%20the%20differences%20between%20RBI%20and%20the%20Centre.%20He'd%20first%20flagged%20this%20issue%20in%20late%202018.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbanking%2Frbi-refused-govts-push-to-transfer-rs-3-lakh-crore-in-2018-ahead-of-general-election-viral-acharya%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Watch%3A%20Kohli%20Gives%20Medal%20To%20Nepal%20Star%2C%20Then%20Breaks%20Into%20Laughter%20With%20SKY%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20cricket%20team%20attained%20its%20first%20target%20at%20the%20Asia%20Cup%202023%20on%20Monday%20-%20that%20is%20to%20qualify%20for%20the%20Super%204%20stage.%20After%20its%20first%20game%20against%20Pakistan%20got%20washed%20out%20due%20to%20rain%2C%20India%20needed%20a%20solid%20win%20against%20Nepal%20to%20boost%20their%20confidence.%20Though%20they%20won%20by%2010%20wickets%2C%20India%20have%20a%20lot%20of%20points%20to%20ponder%20upon.%20India%20captain%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Rohit%20Sharma%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F857-rohit-sharma-playerprofile%5C%22%3ERohit%20Sharma%3C%2Fa%3E%20won%20the%20toss%20and%20elected%20to%20field%20first%2C%20but%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Kushal%20Bhurtel%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F111710-kushal-bhurtel-playerprofile%5C%22%3EKushal%20Bhurtel%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Aasif%20Sheikh%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F112125-aasif-sheikh-playerprofile%5C%22%3EAasif%20Sheikh%3C%2Fa%3E%20got%20quick%20runs%20with%20help%20from%20the%20Indian%20fielders%2C%20who%20dropped%20three%20catches%20in%20the%20first%20five%20overs.%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Shreyas%20Iyer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcric