%20got%20in%20the%20caste%20based%20social%20structure%2C%20which%20is%20unequal%20and%20oppressive%3F%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNo%20one%20intends%20to%20chop%20off%20the%20head%2C%20but%20one%20needs%20to%20cure%20the%20infection%20with%20equal%20rights%20and%20dignity%20to%20all.%20The%20only%20cure%20to%20all%20these%20infections%20is%20the%20Constitution%20to%20which%20your%20organization%20and%20you%20are%20against.%20You%20are%20from%20Karnataka%2C%20please%20spread%20the%20preachings%20of%20Guru%20Basavanna%2C%20it%20will%20help%20us%20built%20a%20more%20equitable%20society%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Kharge%20posted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20latest%20post%20BL%20Santosh%20responded%20saying%20%26quot%3BLeftists%2C%20Naxals%2C%20Urban%20Naxals%20many%20of%20whom%20are%20in%20your%20close%20circles%20exploited%20the%20situation.%20Think%20with%20which%20way%20you%20want%20to%20associate%20with.%20This%20country%20%26amp%3B%20civilisation%20has%20robust%20internal%20correction%20mechanism%20which%20it%20has%20exhibited%20from%20time%20to%20time.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20DMK%20leader%20Udhayanidhi%20Stalin%20on%20Saturday%20said%20that%20Sanatan%20Dharma%20should%20not%20merely%20be%20opposed%20but%20eradicated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFew%20things%20cannot%20be%20opposed%2C%20they%20should%20only%20be%20abolished.%20We%20can't%20oppose%20Dengue%2C%20mosquitoes%2C%20Malaria%2C%20or%20coronavirus%2C%20we%20have%20to%20eradicate%20them.%20In%20the%20same%20way%2C%20we%20have%20to%20eradicate%20Sanatana%20(Sanatan%20Dharma).%20Rather%20than%20merely%20opposing%20Sanatana%2C%20it%20should%20be%20eradicated%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeveral%20leaders%20of%20the%20Indian%20diaspora%20came%20down%20on%20the%20DMK%20leader%20and%20condemned%20his%20remarks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%2