0Teachers%20are%20asked%20to%20accept%20the%20government%20as%20their%20guru%20and%20to%20treat%20its%20words%20as%20sacred%20in%20the%20best%20tradition%20of%20Indian%20disciplehood.%20Teachers%20cannot%20have%20a%20mind%20of%20their%20own.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELet%20us%20start%20with%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir.%20Zahoor%20Ahmed%20Bhat%2C%20a%20senior%20secondary%20school%20teacher%20in%20the%20state%20was%20suspended%20a%20day%20after%20he%20argued%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20against%20the%20Union%20government%E2%80%99s%20move%20to%20read%20down%20Article%20370.%20In%20his%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DsJmkUEgHixk%26ab_channel%3DNewsInsider24x7%5C%22%3E6-minute%20argument%3C%2Fa%3E%20before%20the%20court%2C%20he%20said%20that%20after%20August%205%2C%202019%2C%20he%20was%20finding%20it%20difficult%20to%20teach%20the%20constitution%20of%20India%20as%20a%20teacher.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20reality%20of%20Kashmir%20after%20the%20reading%20down%20of%20Article%20370%20is%20a%20violation%20of%20the%20concept%20of%20the%20constitution.%20How%20can%20he%20as%20a%20teacher%20persuade%20his%20students%20about%20the%20sincerity%20of%20the%20promise%20of%20the%20constitution%20when%20his%20students%20find%20their%20lives%20ravaged%20by%20a%20state%20which%20swears%20by%20this%20document%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBhat%20was%20an%20aggrieved%20teacher.%20For%20the%20audacity%20of%C2%A0%20airing%20of%20his%20grief%20in%C2%A0public%2C%20he%20was%20punished.%20While%20writing%20these%20lines%2C%20his%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.greaterkashmir.com%2Ftodays-paper%2Ffront-page%2Fsuspension-order-of-senior-lecturer-withdrawn%5C%22%3Esuspension%20has%20been%20revoked%20after%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20rebuked%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20administration%20for%20its%20highhandedness.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBefore%20him%2C%20Dr.%20Sabyasachi%20Das%2C%20a%20young%20professor%20at%20Ashoka%20University%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feducation%2Fauthor-of-paper-on-possible-manipulation-in-2019-polls-quits-ashoka-university%5C%22%3Ewas%20forced%20to%20resign%20for%20writing%20a%20research%20paper%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Not%20only%20this%2C%20people%20from%20the%20intelligence%20agency%20of%20the%20government%20of%20India%20threatened%20to%20go%20to%20his%20university%20to%20find%20out%20whether%20he%20had%20written%20his%20research%20paper%20as%20part%20of%20any%20conspiracy%20and%20who%20else%20was%20involved%20in%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feducation%2Fteachers-day-india-nep-ncf-muzaffarnagar%5C%22%3EDehumanising%20Gurus%20While%20We%20Grandstand%20as%20a%20Vishwaguru%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrior%20to%20this%20incident%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theweek.in%2Fwire-updates%2Fnational%2F2023%2F06%2F28%2Fdes43-dl-sau-suspension-scholars.html%5C%22%3Efour%20teachers%20of%20the%20Delhi-based%20South%20Asia%20University%20were%20suspended%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20writing%20a%20letter%20to%20the%20administration%20requesting%20it%20to%20take%20a%20sympathetic%20view%20of%20the%20agitation%20of%20the%20students.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAshok%20Sopan%20Dhole%2C%20a%20teacher%20at%20Symbiosis%20Institute%20in%20Pune%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Fcities%2Fpune-news%2Fprominent-pune-college-teacher-arrested-for-allegedly-disrespecting-hindu-gods-college-suspends-him-101691078255504.html%5C%22%3Ewas%20suspended%20and%20jailed%20for%20his%20lectures%20in%20his%20class%3C%2Fa%3E.%20In%20the%20class%20he%20talked%20about%20the%20equality%20of%20all%20religions.%20Earlier%20in%20Kolhapur%2C%20Dr.%20Tejaswini%20Desai%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fkolhapur-tejaswini-desai-academics-solidarity%5C%22%3Eforcibly%20sent%20on%20leave%20due%20to%20a%20remark%20she%20made%20in%20class%3C%2Fa%3E.%20She%20said%20that%20rapists%20can%20belong%20to%20any%20religion%2C%20it%20is%20wrong%20to%20say%20that%20only%20people%20of%20a%20particular%20religion%20or%20community%20are%20rapists.%20A%20police%20complaint%20has%20also%20been%20filed%20against%20her.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20time%20ago%20the%20principal%20and%20a%20teacher%20of%20a%20law%20institute%20in%20Indore%20were%20fired%20from%20their%20job%20and%20sent%20to%20jail%20after%20an%C2%A0%20%E2%80%98objectionable%E2%80%99%20book%20was%20found%20in%20the%20college%20library.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fprofessor-gilbert-sebastian-central-university-of-kerala-suspension-rss%5C%22%3EGilbert%20Sebastian%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20professor%20at%20the%20Central%20University%20of%20Kerala%2C%20was%20suspended%20for%20his%20class%20on%20fascism.%20Doctor%20Rajshree%20Ranawat%20of%20the%20Jodhpur%20University%20was%20suspended%20and%20a%20police%20report%20filed%20against%20her%20for%20holding%20an%20academic%20seminar.%20Haryana%20Central%20University%20teacher%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.counterview.net%2F2017%2F04%2Fmahashwata-devi-stopped-from-being.html%5C%22%3ESnehasata%20Manav%3C%2Fa%3E%20faced%20attacks%20and%20scrutiny%20for%20dramatising%20a%20story%20of%20Mahasweta%20Devi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EForty%20eight%20teachers%20of%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru%20University%20are%20facing%20disciplinary%20action%20of%20the%20administration%20for%20last%20four%20years.%20Scores%20of%20them%20have%20been%20in%20courts%20fighting%20to%20get%20their%20due%20%E2%80%93%20leave%20for%20a%20seminar%20or%20sanction%20for%20a%20fellowship.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApart%20from%20this%2C%20there%20are%20also%20reports%20of%20teachers%20being%20disciplined%20for%20their%20public%20writing.%20There%20are%20teachers%2C%20who%20wish%20to%20remain%20anonymous%2C%20who%20have%20been%20served%20show-cause%20notices%20by%20their%20administrations%20because%20of%20their%20articles.%20The%20number%20of%20such%20teachers%20is%20increasing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20know%20that%20Pratap%20Bhanu%20Mehta%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Findia%2Fpratap-bhanu-mehta-resignation-letter-ashoka-university-7234669%2F%5C%22%3Egently%20told%20by%20his%20board%20at%20the%20Ashoka%20University%20to%20spare%20the%20university%20as%20his%20public%20utterances%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%20creating%20trouble%20for%20it.%20The%20board%20could%20not%20afford%20to%20have%20a%20Vice-Chancellor%20who%20makes%20the%20govenrment%20look%20bad%20through%20his%20writings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20there%20is%20also%20an%20increase%20in%20the%20number%20of%20such%20teachers%20who%20take%20pride%20in%20being%20seen%20as%20the%20propagandists%20of%20the%20government.%20They%20feel%20elated%20in%20the%20company%20of%20the%20%3Cem%3Epracharak%3C%2Fem%3E%20or%20chief%20of%20the%20Rashtriya%20Swayamsevak%20Sangh%2C%20who%20collect%20%3Cem%3Egurudakshina%3C%2Fem%3E%20or%20a%20teacher%E2%80%99s%20honorarium%20for%20it%20and%20treat%20the%20RSS%20flag%20as%20their%20guru.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIs%20it%20any%20wonder%20if%20students%20get%20confused%20about%20these%20two%20types%20of%20teachers%3F%20Closeness%20to%20the%20first%C2%A0%20type%20of%20teacher%E2%80%99s%20can%20be%20harmful%20while%20proximity%20with%20the%20other%20is%20beneficial.%20The%20question%20that%20keeps%20bothering%20them%20is%20whether%20the%20beneficial%20is%20also%20moral.%20This%20dilemma%20is%20practical.%20We%20teachers%20have%20to%20face%20these%20questions%20of%20students.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEspecially%20at%20the%20time%20of%20entering%20PhD%20courses%2C%20researchers%20struggle%20with%20this%20dilemma%3A%20who%20is%20the%20teacher%20they%20should%20select%20as%20their%20supervisor%3F%20It%20should%20also%20come%20as%20no%20surprise%20that%20they%20often%20choose%20the%20teacher%20who%20can%20help%20them%20get%20worldly%20benefits.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20can%20be%20said%20that%20this%20is%20not%20a%20post-2014%20development.%20Even%20earlier%2C%20there%20was%20competition%20among%20students%20for%20the%20patronage%20of%20some%20special%20teachers.%20But%20what%20is%20happening%20now%20is%20very%20different.%20The%20source%20of%20authority%20of%20these%20teachers%20is%20mostly%20their%20proximity%20to%20one%20or%20the%20other%20faction%20of%20the%20RSS.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fculture%2Fteachers-day-rabindranath-tagore-poem-illustrations%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Where%20Knowledge%20Is%20Free%E2%80%99%3A%20On%20Teachers%E2%80%99%20Day%2C%20Reading%20Tagore%E2%80%99s%20Poem%20Through%20Illustrations%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20glory%20of%20the%20teacher%20was%20partly%20due%20to%20his%20indifference%20to%20worldliness%20in%20society.%20There%20was%20a%20sense%20of%20mental%20independence%20which%20people%20associated%20with%20the%20figure%20of%20the%20teacher.%20If%20the%20power%20lies%20in%20political%20authority%2C%20it%20has%20to%20face%20the%20power%20of%20knowledge.%20Teachers%20have%20been%20respected%20for%20their%20independence%20and%20not%20their%20subservience.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20responsibility%20of%20the%20teacher%20is%20to%20acquaint%20the%20students%20with%20the%20traditions%20and%20methods%20of%20the%20existing%20knowledge.%20But%20more%20than%20that%2C%20her%20responsibility%20is%20also%20to%20inculcate%20in%20the%20student%20enough%20courage%20for%20independent%20thinking%20and%20decision%20making.%20Students%20are%20not%20expected%20to%20follow%20popular%20opinion%20but%20to%20examine%20and%20question%20it.%20Teachers%20do%20not%20do%20this%20by%20hiding%20their%20thoughts.%20They%20assure%C2%A0%20the%20students%20that%20they%20can%20have%20their%20disagreement%20with%20their%20ideas%2C%20they%20can%20argue%20with%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20responsibility%20of%20the%20teacher%20towards%20the%20students%20is%20to%20challenge%20them%20to%20step%20out%20of%20their%20safe%20confines%20and%20face%20the%20unfamiliar%20or%20the%20unexpected.%20A%20teacher%20may%20become%20popular%20by%20pandering%20to%20the%20prejudices%20of%20the%20students%2C%20but%20they%20will%20be%20cheating%20on%20their%20duty.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20tasks%20of%20a%20teacher%20is%20to%20prepare%20the%20society%20to%20understand%20and%20examine%20itself.%20This%20is%20integral%20to%20the%20job.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20teacher%20in%20today%E2%80%99s%20India%20cannot%20discharge%20any%20of%20these%20responsibilities%20without%20putting%20herself%20at%20risk.%20Many%20teachers%20have%20taken%20this%20risk%20knowing%20well%20the%20whole%20situation.%20Like%20Hani%20Babu%20or%20Anand%20Teltumbde.%20Many%20teachers%20who%20did%20not%20go%20to%20jail%20like%20them%20are%20facing%C2%A0%20persecution%20of%20different%20types.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELet%20us%20dedicate%20this%20Teachers%E2%80%99%20Day%20to%20these%20teachers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EApoorvanand%20teaches%20at%20Delhi%20University.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693898885000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F09%2F13084433%2FIMG_1352.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feducation%2Fteachers-day-india-government-rss-freedom%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22This%20Teachers'%20Day%2C%20we%20must%20remember%20the%20teachers%20who%20have%20been%20suspended%2C%20penalised%2C%20arrested%2C%20jailed%2C%20or%20forced%20to%20quit%20for%20being%20independent%20and%20teaching%20students%20this%20independence.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feducation%2Fteachers-day-india-government-rss-freedom%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%E2%80%98Doctor%20Who%2C%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%98The%20Crown%E2%80%99%20Star%20Matt%20Smith%20Returns%20to%20London%20Stage%20With%20Ibsen%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98An%20Enemy%20of%20the%20People%E2%80%99%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1