tion%20of%20Rs%2030%20crore.%20Jawan%20is%20all%20set%20to%20hit%20theatres%20soon%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22After%20Vice%20President's%20Comment%2C%20Buzz%20Over%20Women's%20Quota%20In%20Special%20Session%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20bill%20to%20reserve%2033%25%20of%20seats%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20and%20state%20assemblies%20for%20women%20has%20got%20a%20fillip%20after%20Vice%20President%20Jagdeep%20Dhankhar%20said%20on%20Monday%20that%20the%20day%20is%20not%20far%20when%20women%20will%20get%20due%20representation%20in%20the%20country's%20legislatures.%20The%20legislation%20had%20been%20passed%20by%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20in%202010%20but%20lapsed%20after%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20did%20not%20clear%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Vice%20President's%20comment%20has%20sparked%20speculation%20that%20the%20women's%20reservation%20bill%20may%20be%20moved%20during%20the%20special%20session%20of%20parliament%20from%20September%2018-22%2C%20the%20agenda%20for%20which%20is%20yet%20to%20be%20revealed.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Tuesday%2C%20Telangana%20MLC%20and%20Chief%20Minister%20K%20Chandrasekhar%20Rao's%20daughter%20K%20Kavitha%20also%20wrote%20a%20letter%20to%20presidents%20of%20all%2047%20political%20parties%20with%20representation%20in%20parliament%20and%20urged%20them%20to%20set%20aside%20political%20differences%20and%20prioritise%20the%20passage%20of%20the%20bill%20in%20the%20upcoming%20special%20session.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20bill%20seeking%20to%20reserve%2033%25%20seats%20for%20women%20was%20first%20moved%20by%20the%20Deve%20Gowda%20government%20in%201996.%20The%20UPA%20government%20then%20reintroduced%20the%20legislation%2C%20officially%20known%20as%20the%20Constitution%20(One%20Hundred%20and%20Eighth%20Amendment)%20Bill%2C%20in%202008.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20legislation%20was%20passed%20by%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20in%202010%2C%20but%20the%2015th%20Lok%20Sabha%20could%20not%20pass%20the%20bill%20and%20it%20lapsed%20following%20its%20dissolution%20in%202014.%20Parties%20such%20as%20the%20Samajwadi%20Party%20and%20the%20Rashtriya%20Janata%20Dal%20have%20opposed%20the%20bill%20in%20its%20current%20form%2C%20demanding%20%26quot%3Ba%20quota%20within%20the%20quota%26quot%3B.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20parties%20have%20argued%20that%20the%20reservation%20should%20provide%20for%20a%20quota%20for%20Dalit%2C%20backward%2C%20extremely%20backward%20and%20minority%20communities.%20An%20RJD%20leader%20had%20said%20that%20the%20party%20does%20not%20have%20a%20problem%20if%20the%20reservation%20for%20women%20needs%20to%20be%20hiked%20to%2050%25%20to%20provide%20a%20quota%20to%20these%20sections%2C%20but%20it%20is%20%E2%80%9Cmeaningless%E2%80%9D%20without%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBeing%20a%20constitutional%20amendment%2C%20the%20bill%20will%20require%20the%20support%20of%20two-thirds%20of%20the%20members%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha.%20It%20was%20part%20of%20the%20BJP's%20election%20manifesto%20in%202014%20and%2C%20sources%20said%2C%20its%20passage%20is%20likely%20to%20benefit%20the%20party%20by%20helping%20it%20consolidate%20the%20votes%20of%20women.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20at%20an%20event%20on%20%26quot%3BWomen's%20Participation%20in%20Nation%20Building%26quot%3B%20at%20a%20college%20in%20Jaipur%20on%20Monday%2C%20Vice%20President%20Dhankhar%20had%20said%20that%20the%20day%20is%20not%20far%20when%20women%20will%20get%20their%20due%20representation%20in%20Parliament%20and%20legislative%20assemblies%20through%20an%20amendment%20to%20the%20Constitution.%20He%20said%20that%20if%20this%20reservation%20is%20given%20soon%2C%20India%20will%20become%20a%20world%20power%20before%202047.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Dhankhar%20asserted%20that%20the%20sky%20is%20the%20limit%20for%20women%20as%20they%20are%20creating%20new%20models%20of%20success%20in%20every%20field%2C%20including%20administration%2C%20the%20corporate%20world%2C%20and%20the%20Army.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20her%20letter%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20Bharat%20Rashtra%20Samithi%20Leader%20K%20Kavitha%2C%20who%20is%20also%20a%20former%20Lok%20Sabha%20MP%2C%20asserted%20%26quot%3Bthat%20increased%20women's%20representation%20is%20not%20a%20matter%20of%20exclusivity%20but%20a%20means%20to%20build%20a%20more%20equitable%20and%20balanced%20political%20landscape%26quot%3B.%20She%20urged%20all%20parties%20to%20recognise%20the%20urgency%20of%20this%20matter%20and%20back%20the%20women's%20reservation%20bill.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20written%20reply%20to%20a%20question%20in%20July%2C%20the%20Centre%20had%20told%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20that%20the%20women's%20reservation%20bill%20requires%20%26quot%3Bcareful%20consideration%26quot%3B%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20consensus%20among%20all%20political%20parties%20before%20it%20is%20brought%20to%20Parliament.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20reply%2C%20Law%20Minister%20Arjun%20Ram%20Meghwal%20had%20said%20gender%20justice%20is%20an%20important%20commitment%20of%20the%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20March%2C%20the%20Congress%20had%20asked%20the%20BJP%20to%20make%20its%20stand%20clear%20on%20the%20bill%20and%20demanded%20that%20it%20be%20tabled%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693897920000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2019-07%2Frtvrrj68_parliament-generic-pti_625x300_23_July_19.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwomens-reservation-bill-special-session-womens-quota-bill-in-special-session-vice-presidents-comment-sparks-buzz-4360659%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20bill%20to%20reserve%2033%25%20of%20seats%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20and%20state%20assemblies%20for%20women%20got%20a%20fillip%20on%20Monday%20when%20Vice%20President%20Jagdeep%20Dhankhar%20said%20the%20day%20is%20not%20far%20when%20women%20will%20get%20due%20representation%20in%20the%20country's%20legislatures.%22%2C%