ess-standard.com%2Famp%2Findustry%2Fauto%2Fauto-sales-up-9-in-august-pv-inventory-at-an-all-time-high-fada-123090500267_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Findustry%2Fauto%2Fauto-sales-up-9-in-august-pv-inventory-at-an-all-time-high-fada-123090500267_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22As%20Bengal%20Govt's%20Political%20Tussle%20With%20the%20Union%20Plays%20Out%2C%20Children's%20Nutrition%20Has%20Suffered%20Most%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F05111134%2F49423100271_a6eb794c72_c.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3EKolkata%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20At%20the%20heart%20of%20the%20expansive%20Shonagachi%20Tea%20Estate%20in%20north%20Bengal%2C%20the%20Shishualaya%20%E2%80%93%20literally%20%E2%80%98abode%20for%20children%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%93%20was%20a%20key%20place%20for%20workers.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHere%2C%20children%20under%20six%20received%20their%20early%20education%20and%20meals.%20But%20of%20late%2C%20the%20rice%20and%20dal%20in%20the%20pots%20seem%20to%20be%20running%20out%20faster%20than%20usual.%20Eggs%2C%20which%20used%20to%20be%20served%20earlier%20are%20now%20a%20distant%20memory.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ERima%20Oraon%2C%20an%20Anganwadi%20worker%2C%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20hide%20her%20frustration.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20enough%20money%20for%20rice%20and%20dal%20and%20salt%2C%20let%20alone%20eggs.%20And%20the%20government%20insists%20that%20only%20if%20we%20finish%20online%20accounting%20and%20record%20keeping%20for%20the%20earlier%20meals%20can%20we%20get%20money%20for%20future%20meals.%20Don%E2%80%99t%20they%20understand%20the%20challenges%20we%20face%3F%E2%80%9D%20she%20asks.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20children%20around%20Rima%20are%20in%20various%20stages%20of%20play.%20Some%20have%20hoisted%20themselves%20up%20on%20a%20window.%20Others%20are%20running%20around.%20Maybe%20there%20will%20be%20some%20lessons%2C%20maybe%20there%20will%20be%20a%20meal.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERima%20was%20told%20she%20would%20get%20an%20Android%20phone%20that%20would%20help%20her%20with%20the%20mandatory%20online%20record%20keeping.%20But%20no%20such%20phone%20arrived.%20She%20initially%20visited%20cyber%20cafes%20but%20they%20proved%20very%20expensive%2C%20leading%20her%20to%20abandon%20the%20process%20entirely.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20an%20Anganwadi%20worker%2C%20Rima%20is%20in%20charge%20of%20mothers%20and%20their%20children%20of%20up%20to%20five%20years.%20%3Cspan%3EThe%20mothers%20and%20children%20of%20many%20as%20262%20households%20depend%20on%20this%20Shishualaya%E2%80%99s%20meals%20everyday.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ES%3Cspan%3Eince%20June%2C%20funds%20had%20dried%20up%2C%20leaving%20Rima%20to%20borrow%3C%2Fspan%3E%20from%20local%20kirana%20stores.%20Eventually%2C%20the%20shopkeepers%E2%80%99%20goodwill%20waned.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERima%20has%20told%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20Integrated%20Child%20Development%20Services%20authorities%20that%20she%20has%20only%20been%20feeding%20khichdi%20to%20children.%20But%20her%20pleas%20have%20not%20led%20to%20action.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAt%20lunch%20time%20when%20%3Cem%3EThe%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3EWire%3C%2Fem%3E%20visited%2C%20some%20children%20chimed%2C%20%E2%80%9CDidi%2C%20we%20want%20eggs.%E2%80%9D%20Rima%20says%20the%20household%20must%20suspects%20that%20she%20makes%20off%20with%20the%20money%20for%20eggs.%20%E2%80%9CBut%20that%20is%20not%20true%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feconomy%2Fbudget-nutrition-anganwadi-mid-day-meal-schemes%5C%22%3EThis%20Year%E2%80%99s%20Budget%20Is%20Critical%20to%20Ensure%20a%20Comprehensive%20Nutrition%20Response%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOver%20the%20past%20three%20months%2C%20a%20persistent%20demand%20for%20eggs%20has%20become%20a%20source%20of%20concern%20for%20Anganwadi%20workers%20across%20the%20state.%20The%20initial%20plan%20of%20the%20Bengal%20government%20had%20aimed%20to%20provide%20one%20whole%20egg%20three%20times%20a%20week%20to%20children%20attending%20approximately%20the%20120%2C000%20Anganwadi%20centres%20across%20the%20state.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETo%20support%20this%20initiative%2C%20a%20daily%20allocation%20of%20Rs%206.50%20per%20child%20was%20decided.%20Eggs%20would%20be%20given%20on%20Monday%2C%20Wednesday%2C%20and%20Friday.%20Pregnant%20mothers%20were%20also%20included%20in%20the%20plan%2C%20with%20an%20allocation%20of%20Rs%207.34%20for%20eggs%20and%20vegetables%2C%20supplemented%20by%20an%20extra%20Rs%200.84%20for%20potatoes.%20For%20Tuesday%2C%20Thursday%2C%20and%20Saturday%2C%20the%20allocation%20for%20children%20was%20adjusted%20to%20half%20an%20egg%2C%20at%20a%20cost%20of%20Rs%204.34%2C%20inclusive%20of%20Rs.%201.09%20for%20vegetables.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20February%20of%202023%2C%20Smriti%20Irani%2C%20the%20Union%20minister%20of%20women%20and%20child%20development%2C%20raised%20concerns%20over%20the%20appropriate%20utilisation%20of%20funds%20designated%20for%20the%20ICDS%20scheme%20in%20Bengal.%20Bengal%20minister%20of%20state%20(independent%20charge)%20of%20the%20same%20department%2C%20Shashi%20Panja%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fcity%2Fkolkata%2Firani-panja-in-war-of-words-over-funds%2Farticleshow%2F97615219.cms%5C%22%3Esaid%20there%20was%20no%20such%20ICDS%20money%20lying%20unspent%3C%2Fa%3E.%20She%20said%20that%20the%20Bengal%20government%20has%20instead%20been%20raising%20concerns%20about%20reduced%20fund%20allocations%20and%20delayed%20disbursements%20for%20the%20ICDS.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESince%20June%20this%20year%2C%20the%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20government%20has%20entirely%20stopped%20disbursing%20financial%20support%20for%20essentials%20like%20eggs%20and%20vegetables%20under%20the%20ICDS%2C%20leading%20to%20a%20lack%20of%20crucial%20nutritional%20aid%20for%20young%20children%20and%20expectant%20mothers.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20state%20government%20is%20pressuring%20Anganwadi%20workers%20to%20manage%20multiple%20centres%20since%20new%20hiring%20has%20practically%20ceased.%20How%20many%20centres%20can%20an%20Anganwadi%20worker%20effectively%20handle%20when%20she%20also%20needs%20to%20prepare%20and%20provide%20nourishing%20meals%20to%20mothers%20and%20children%2C%20and%20accompany%20them%20to%20nearby%20hospitals%3F%20Consequently%2C%20even%20though%20the%20centres%20are%20technically%20operational%20on%20paper%2C%20the%20workers%20are%20facing%20significant%20challenges%20in%20running%20them.%20Due%20to%20a%20lack%20of%20government%20funds%2C%20arranging%20food%20has%20become%20a%20struggle%2C%E2%80%9D%20stated%20Ratna%20Dutta%2C%20general%20secretary%20of%20the%20Paschimbanga%20Rajya%20ICDS%20Karmi%20Samiti%2C%20an%20organisation%20with%20a%20membership%20of%20over%2070%2C000%20workers.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20the%20dispute%20between%20the%20state%20and%20central%20authorities%20continues%2C%20it%20is%20Anganwadi%20workers%20like%20Rima%20Oraon%20who%20keep%20borrowing%20money%20to%20ensure%20that%20children%20continue%20eating.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CDuring%20the%20COVID%20pandemic%2C%20many%20centres%20were%20forced%20to%20shut%20down%2C%20which%20was%20devastating%20for%20children%20and%20expecting%20mothers.%20As%20the%20dispute%20between%20the%20central%20and%20state%20governments%20continues%2C%20these%20centres%20are%20again%20facing%20critical%20challenges.%20The%20government%20must%20ensure%20these%20facilities%20remain%20functional%20regardless%20of%20the%20ongoing%20circumstances%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Sabir%20Ahmed%2C%20a%20researcher%20working%20on%20maternal%20and%20child%20health%2C%20nutrition%2C%20and%20education%20at%20the%20Pratichi%20Trust%20founded%20by%20Nobel%20laureate%20Amartya%20Sen.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAcross%20the%20state%2C%20many%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftv9bangla.com%2Fvideos%2Fprotest-in-anganwadi-center-in-debra-876489.html%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EAnganwadi%20centres%20are%20in%20dire%20condition%20without%20proper%20kitchens%20or%20toilets%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20In%20recent%20times%2C%20there%20were%20multiple%20reports%20on%20local%20media%20of%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftv9bangla.com%2Fwest-bengal%2Fpaschim-medinipur%2Fanganwari-centre-has-no-concrete-building-children-education-going-with-risk-au38-775658.html%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eunhygienic%20and%20contaminated%20food%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20being%20provided%20to%20children%20and%20expecting%20mothers.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ELike%20Rima%2C%20other%20Anganwadi%20workers%20in%20the%20state%20have%20also%20made%20complaints%20of%20their%20inability%20to%20update%20the%20Poshan%20Tracker%20%E2%80%93%20the%20real-time%20mobile%20application%20brought%20by%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Women%20and%20Child%20Development%20to%20track%20nutritional%20parameters.%20Anganwadi%20workers%20were%20expected%20to%20note%20down%20key%20parameters%20including%20height%2C%20weight%20and%20the%20circumference%20of%20a%20child%E2%80%99s%20arms.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20West%20Bengal%2C%20an%20Anganwadi%20worker%20receives%20a%20monthly%20salary%20of%20Rs%208%2C250%2C%20while%20a%20helper%20receives%20Rs%206%2C300.%20The%20workers%20are%20advocating%20for%20the%20implementation%20of%20a%20minimum%20wage%2C%20provision%20of%20smartphones%2C%20and%20an%20additional%20Rs%20500%20per%20month%20for%20internet%20connectivity%20to%20update%20the%20Poshan%20app.%20As%20per%20Poshan%20Tracker%2C%20the%20state%20has%20109%2C454%20registered%20workers%20and%20another%2098%2C787%20helpers.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20the%20Union%20government%20has%20allocated%20funds%20to%20procure%20smartphones%20for%20the%20Anganwadi%20workers%2C%20the%20West%20Bengal%20government%20is%20yet%20to%20start%20initiative.%20Many%20Anganwadi%20workers%20%3Cem%3EThe%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3EWire%3C%2Fem%3E%20spoke%20to%20said%20the%20lack%20of%20a%20smart%20phone%2C%20lack%20of%20connectivity%20and%20language%20barriers%20make%20it%20an%20impossible%20exercise.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20scheme%20cannot%20be%20stalled%20for%20any%20reason.%20It%20is%20one%20of%20the%20most%20important%20flagship%20projects%20in%20the%20country%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20the%20former%20editor%20of%20%3Cem%3EAnandabazar%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3EPatrika%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20Anirban%20Chattopadhyay%2C%20who%20has%20been%20working%20on%20developmental%20economics.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20is%20a%20huge%20problem%20of%20infrastructure%2C%20the%20workers%20are%20also%20ignored.%20Our%20civil%20society%20is%20silent%20on%20these%20issues.%20The%20project%20must%20be%20continued%20at%20any%20cost%2C%20now%20is%20not%20the%20time%20to%20see%20who%20is%20at%20fault%2C%20the%20centre%20or%20the%20state%2C%E2%80%9D%20added%20Chattopadhyay.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ETranslated%20from%20the%20Bengali%20original%20by%20Aparna%20Bhattacharya.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693892827000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F05111134%2F49423100271_a6eb794c72_c.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fposhan-tracker-anganwadi-icds-bengal-centre%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22As%20the%20dispute%20between%20the%20state%20and%20central%20authorities%20continues%2C%20Anganwadi%20workers%20are%20left%20borrowing%20money%20to%20ensure%20ICDS%20beneficiaries%20like%20mothers%20and%20their%20young%20children%20continue%20to%20get%20meals.%22%2C%2