%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693886007000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-103376793%2Cimgsize-885543.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Findore%2Frajnath-bats-for-shivraj-calls-him-dhoni-of-politics%2Farticleshow%2F103376748.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Defence%20minister%20Rajnath%20Singh%20compared%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20chief%20minister%20Shivraj%20Singh%20Chouhan%20to%20cricketer%20MS%20Dhoni%2C%20saying%20that%20Chouhan%20is%20like%20Dhoni%20in%20politics%20as%20he%20always%20finishes%20with%20a%20win.%20Singh%20praised%20Chouhan's%20work%20for%20the%20people%20and%20accused%20former%20CM%20Kamal%20Nath%20of%20stopping%20welfare%20schemes%20during%20the%20Congress%20government.%20Singh%20also%20appealed%20to%20people%20to%20vote%20for%20BJP%20and%20predicted%20a%20defeat%20for%20the%20opposition%20INDIA%20alliance.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TNN%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Findore%2Frajnath-bats-for-shivraj-calls-him-dhoni-of-politics%2Farticleshow%2F103376748.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Whether%20Polls%20Are%20Sooner%20or%20Later%2C%20INDIA%20Must%20Face%20Fundamental%20Questions%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F01145303%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-09-01-at-1.39.00-PM-1.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20has%20taken%20nine%20years%20for%20the%20disparate%20Opposition%20parties%20to%20realise%20that%20if%20they%20do%20not%20hang%20together%20they%20will%20hang%20separately%20to%20fight%20the%20monolithic%20and%20powerful%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party.%20And%20the%20INDIA%20block%20they%20have%20formed%20offers%20perhaps%20the%20best%20opportunity%20to%20take%20on%20the%20mighty%20ruling%20party%2C%20they%20all%20seem%20to%20feel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20week%2C%20out%20of%20their%20first%20major%20conclave%20in%20Mumbai%20emerged%20the%20most%20extraordinary%20images%20seen%20in%20India%20for%20some%20time.%20Long-term%20rivals%20in%20the%20same%20room%20%E2%80%94%20CPI(M)%20and%20Trinamool%20Congress%2C%20AAP%20and%20the%20Congress%20%E2%80%94%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack.com%2Fredirect%2Fa634b669-ec6c-40a4-9756-be3210287911%3Fj%3DeyJ1IjoiaHpuMnUifQ.MQOquijPBw98XVYBc9m195DW7Qx9ruSvngQYE7EwHGg%5C%22%20data-saferedirecturl%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Furl%3Fq%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fsubstack.com%2Fredirect%2Fa634b669-ec6c-40a4-9756-be3210287911%3Fj%253DeyJ1IjoiaHpuMnUifQ.MQOquijPBw98XVYBc9m195DW7Qx9ruSvngQYE7EwHGg%26amp%3Bsource%3Dgmail%26amp%3Bust%3D1693971091038000%26amp%3Busg%3DAOvVaw2EcraKa4EVXnMKSuVS6avR%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etying%20a%20rakhi%20to%20Uddhav%20Thackeray%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20the%20regional%20parties%20putting%20aside%20their%20innate%20hostility%20to%20the%20Congress.%20These%20are%20optics%2C%20for%20sure%2C%20but%20perceptions%20do%20matter%20and%20certainly%20the%20prime%20minister%20and%20his%20party%20colleagues%20take%20this%20grouping%20seriously%20enough%20to%20continuously%20mock%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnited%20Opposition%20fronts%20have%20been%20seen%20in%20the%20past.%20The%20Janata%20Party%2C%20formed%20within%20weeks%20of%20the%20Emergency%20being%20lifted%20in%201977%2C%20had%20trounced%20Indira%20Gandhi.%20It%20contained%20members%20of%20the%20old%20Congress%2C%20the%20socialists%20and%20the%20Jan%20Sangh.%20The%20National%20Front%20of%201989%2C%20which%20was%20spearheaded%20by%20V.P.%20Singh%E2%80%99s%20Janata%20Dal%20and%20the%20Telugu%20Desam%20Party%2C%20formed%20two%20governments%20in%20two%20years.%20The%20United%20Front%20of%2013%20parties%20which%20was%20formed%20after%20the%201996%20elections%20also%20formed%20two%20governments.%20Every%20one%20of%20these%20experiments%20failed%20due%20to%20internal%20contradictions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20no%20saying%20that%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%20will%20also%20not%20dissolve.%20Nor%20can%20anyone%20guarantee%20that%20even%20before%20the%20elections%2C%20internal%20dissensions%20will%20not%20crop%20up%20on%20issues%20such%20as%20fighting%20state%20elections%20or%20seat%20sharing%20for%202024.%20Already%2C%20the%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20has%20been%20making%20strong%20statements%20attacking%20the%20Congress%20government%20in%20Chhattisgarh%2C%20which%20the%20latter%20is%20not%20amused%20about.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22'Ready%20to%20Face%20Raids'%3A%20INDIA%20Parties%20Resolve%20to%20Fight%20Polls%20Together%2C%20Announce%204%20Committees%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Findia-election-lok-sabha-together-four-committees%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Ready%20to%20Face%20Raids%E2%80%99%3A%20INDIA%20Parties%20Resolve%20to%20Fight%20Polls%20Together%2C%20Announce%204%20Committees%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeat%20sharing%20and%20putting%20up%20joint%20candidates%20will%20pose%20an%20even%20bigger%20challenge.%20Will%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20agree%20to%20work%20for%20a%20CPI(M)%20candidate%20in%20West%20Bengal%3F%20Will%20Congress%20workers%20support%20an%20NCP%20candidate%20in%20Maharashtra%3F%20How%20will%20parties%20convince%20their%20cadre%20to%20campaign%20for%20rivals%3F%20The%20Congress%20has%20always%20regarded%20Sharad%20Pawar%20with%20suspicion.%20His%20nephew%20Ajit%20Pawar%E2%80%99s%20departure%20to%20the%20Shiv%20Sena-BJP%20government%20has%20only%20added%20to%20it.%20When%20the%20two%20met%20recently%2C%20the%20Congress%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack.com%2Fredirect%2F285baf74-5a45-4ad8-a754-929bf65ab0b7%3Fj%3DeyJ1IjoiaHpuMnUifQ.MQOquijPBw98XVYBc9m195DW7Qx9ruSvngQYE7EwHGg%5C%22%20data-saferedirecturl%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Furl%3Fq%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fsubstack.com%2Fredirect%2F285baf74-5a45-4ad8-a754-929bf65ab0b7%3Fj%253DeyJ1IjoiaHpuMnUifQ.MQOquijPBw98XVYBc9m195DW7Qx9ruSvngQYE7EwHGg%26amp%3Bsource%3Dgmail%26amp%3Bust%3D1693971091038000%26amp%3Busg%3DAOvVaw0V9NSXpnWrnBH-htiCRraX%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edemanded%20answers%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Bihar%20is%20going%20to%20be%20another%20challenge.%20Tejashwi%20Yadav%20and%20his%20father%20Lalu%20Prasad%20Yadav%20are%20well%20disposed%20towards%20the%20Congress%2C%20but%20is%20Nitish%20Kumar%3F%20And%20where%20does%20Kumar%20stand%2C%20anyway%3F%20He%20was%20very%20much%20present%20at%20the%20Mumbai%20meeting%2C%20but%20he%20has%20ambitions%20of%20his%20own.%20He%20will%20not%20be%20amused%20if%20he%20sees%20another%20leader%20emerge.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20are%20not%20arbitrary%2C%20abstract%20questions.%20They%20will%20have%20to%20be%20tackled%20very%20soon.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20most-asked%20question%20today%20is%2C%20whether%20INDIA%20will%20be%20able%20to%20defeat%20the%20BJP.%20No%20one%20can%20give%20a%20firm%20answer.%20The%20BJP%20is%20not%20going%20to%20sit%20idle%20and%20will%20have%20plans%20of%20its%20own.%20While%20the%20conclave%20was%20going%20on%2C%20the%20government%20called%20a%20special%20five%20day%20session%20of%20parliament%20and%20speculation%20is%20on%20about%20what%20the%20government%20intends%20to%20announce%20in%20it.%20Simultaneously%2C%20a%20committee%20has%20been%20set%20up%20to%20discuss%20One%20Nation%20One%20Election%20%E2%80%95%20simultaneous%20elections%20to%20the%20states%20and%20the%20Centre.%20The%20BJP%20has%20set%20the%20political%20agenda%20and%20the%20Opposition%20parties%20are%20busy%20attacking%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20elections%20get%20closer%2C%20will%20the%20BJP%20pull%20a%20stunt%20to%20galvanise%20its%20supporters%20and%20consolidate%20its%20vote%3F%20Already%2C%20questions%20are%20being%20asked%20about%20the%20Pulwama%20attack%20in%202019%20in%20which%2040%20Indian%20soldiers%20died%20and%20which%20led%20to%20the%20so-called%20%E2%80%98surgical%20strike%E2%80%99%20which%20then%20enthused%20voters%2C%20appealing%20to%20nationalist%20sentiments.%20What%20will%20be%20the%20enthusing%20move%20this%20time%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22BJP's%20Propaganda%2C%20Probe%20Agencies%20and%20Partisan%20Media%3A%20The%20Challenges%20Before%20Opposition's%20INDIA%20Bloc%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fbjps-propaganda-probe-agencies-and-partisan-media-the-challenges-for-opposition-india-bloc%5C%22%3EBJP%E2%80%99s%20Propaganda%2C%20Probe%20Agencies%20and%20Partisan%20Media%3A%20The%20Challenges%20Before%20Opposition%E2%80%99s%20INDIA%20Bloc%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20INDIA%20alliance%20has%20just%20been%20set%20up.%20What%20if%20elections%20are%20called%20in%20the%20Parliament%20session%20%E2%80%94%20does%20it%20have%20the%20wherewithal%20to%20fight%20as%20a%20joint%20front%3F%20The%20BJP%20may%20be%20counting%20on%20surprise.%20Two%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack.com%2Fredirect%2F45d8bdfe-b42e-4b8c-be9e-32bc5f57ef90%3Fj%3DeyJ1IjoiaHpuMnUifQ.MQOquijPBw98XVYBc9m195DW7Qx9ruSvngQYE7EwHGg%5C%22%20data-saferedirecturl%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Furl%3Fq%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fsubstack.com%2Fredirect%2F45d8bdfe-b42e-4b8c-be9e-32bc5f57ef90%3Fj%253DeyJ1IjoiaHpuMnUifQ.MQOquijPBw98XVYBc9m195DW7Qx9ruSvngQYE7EwHGg%26amp%3Bsource%3Dgmail%26amp%3Bust%3D1693971091038000%26amp%3Busg%3DAOvVaw0cchO73mPFF7HpOv_SjhXL%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Evoter%20surveys%C2%A0%3C%2Fa%3Ehave%20suggested%20that%20if%20the%20elections%20were%20to%20be%20held%20now%2C%20the%20BJP%20and%20its%20allies%20will%20win.%20Of%20course%2C%20surveys%20often%20go%20wrong%20%E2%80%94%20the%20BJP%20was%20supposed%20to%20win%20in%20Karnataka%20recently%20and%20earlier%20in%20West%20Bengal%2C%20which%20was%20highlighted%20by%20television%20channels.%20Yet%2C%20the%20fundamental%20question%20of%20INDIA%E2%80%99s%20preparedness%20remains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bonhomie%20between%20various%20parties%20was%20heartwarming%2C%20but%20clearly%2C%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%20has%20its%20work%20cut%20out%20ahead%20of%20the%20elections%2C%20whenever%20they%20are%20held.%20Indeed%2C%20an%20earlier%20election%20will%20probably%20work%20in%20its%20favour%20because%20there%20will%20not%20be%20any%20time%20for%20differences%20to%20crop%20up.%20It%20may%20not%20win%20%E2%80%94%20and%20chances%20are%2C%20it%20won%E2%80%99t%20%E2%80%94%20but%20the%20front%20can%20give%20the%20BJP%20a%20tough%20fight.%20This%20time%20round%2C%20the%20BJP%20will%20not%20find%20the%20going%20so%20easy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20article%20was%20first%20published%20on%20The%20India%20Cable%20%E2%80%93%20a%20premium%20newsletter%20from%20The%20Wire%20%26amp%3B%20Galileo%20Ideas%20%E2%80%93%20and%20has%20been%20republished%20here.%20To%20subscribe%20to%20The%20India%20Cable%2C%20click%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheindiacable.com%2F%5C%22%3Ehere%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693885653000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F01145303%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-09-01-at-1.39.00-PM-1.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fwhether-polls-are-sooner-or-later-india-must-face-fundamental-questions%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20bonhomie%20between%20various%20parties%20was%20heartwarming%2C%20but%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%20has%20its%20work%20cut%20out%20ahead%20of%20the%20elections.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fwhether-polls-are-sooner-or-later-india-must-face-fundamental-questions%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%224%20alleged%20gunmen%20have%20been%20killed%20in%20a%20clash%20with%20security%20forces%20in%20Mexican%20border%20city%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A