24%2Fbranded_news%2F1600D%2Fproduction%2F_130952109_fizzatlatitude.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fentertainment-arts-66572766%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Frustrated%20by%20the%20music%20industry%2C%20four%20solo%20singers%20made%20an%20album%20together%20in%20secret%20in%20two%20weeks.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A16%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fentertainment-arts-66572766%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-bbc-co-uk.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fentertainment-arts-66572766.amp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fentertainment-arts-66572766.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Dehumanising%20Gurus%20While%20We%20Grandstand%20as%20a%20Vishwaguru%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F02%2F05110939%2FIMG_0051.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EToday%2C%20September%205%2C%20is%20celebrated%20as%20Teachers%E2%80%99%20Day%20in%20India.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Bihar%20government%20recently%20came%20out%20with%20a%20detailed%20Request%20For%20Proposal%20(RFP)%20for%20the%20%E2%80%98Empanelment%20of%20Professional%20Educational%20Institutes%20for%20Academic%20Support%20in%20Government%20Senior%20Secondary%20School.%E2%80%99%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%20This%20is%20for%20its%209%2C000%20senior%20secondary%20schools%2C%20in%20all%20districts%20divided%20into%20four%20zones%2C%20for%20the%20effective%20implementation%20of%20the%20programme.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20the%20%E2%80%98academic%E2%80%99%20gloss%20quickly%20wears%20off%2C%20beginning%20with%20listing%20the%20expected%20tasks%20of%20providing%20academic%20support%2C%20taking%20%E2%80%98academic%20sessions%E2%80%99%2C%20to%20bidding%20with%20the%20%E2%80%98lowest%20cost%20method%E2%80%99%2C%20for%20taking%20regular%20physical%20or%20virtual%20classes%20during%20the%20school%20time.%20Moreover%20the%20bidding%20rate%20is%20separately%20asked%20for%20physical%20or%20virtual%20classes%2C%20and%20for%20each%20of%20the%20listed%20subjects%20%E2%80%93%20Science%20(Physics%2C%20Chemistry%2C%20Botany%20and%20Zoology)%2C%20Math%2C%20Computer%20Science%2C%20Hindi%20or%20English.%20The%20monthly%20progress%20report%20requires%20the%20syllabus%20covered%2C%20the%20number%20and%20duration%20of%20lectures%20taken%2C%20and%20the%20attendance%20of%20lecturers%20and%20students.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIndeed%2C%20by%20the%20time%20we%20get%20to%20page%2011%20of%20the%20RFP%2C%20the%20plan%20is%20clear%2C%20the%20language%20cold%20and%20bold.%20It%20demands%20an%20Earnest%20Money%20Deposit%20of%20Rs%205%20lakh%20by%20a%20bidder%20registered%20under%20the%20Bihar%20Coaching%20Institute%20(C%26amp%3BR)%20Act%2C%202010%2C%20with%20an%C2%A0%20%E2%80%9Caverage%20annual%20turnover%20of%20INR%2010%20crore%20or%20more%20in%20the%20last%20three%20financial%20years%20as%20of%2031st%20Mar%202022%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3EFrom%20coaching%20business%20(%3Cem%3Esic%3C%2Fem%3E).%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAfter%20several%20details%20of%20the%20financial%20kind%2C%20including%20on%20fraud%20and%20corrupt%20practices%2C%20a%20small%20note%20at%20the%20end%20of%20page%2020%20says%20that%20the%20minimum%20qualification%20of%20the%20faculty%20should%20be%20%E2%80%9CPost%20Graduation%2FB.Tech%2For%20equivalent%20course%20in%20the%20subject%20concerned%E2%80%9D.%20This%20does%20not%20include%20a%20professional%20education%20degree%20such%20as%20a%20B.Ed.%20or%20an%20M.Ed.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EA%20Deeply%20Disturbing%20Teachers%E2%80%99%20Day%C2%A0%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWe%20are%20witnessing%20a%20deeply%20disturbing%20Teachers%E2%80%99%20Day%2C%20after%20most%20states%20have%20completely%20buckled%20under%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feducation%2Fnep-higher-education-kasturirangan-education-ministry%5C%22%3Elure%20and%20guidance%20of%20NEP%202020%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20to%20aggressively%20privatise%20their%20public%20education%20systems%20through%20all%20kinds%20of%20means%2C%20and%20abandon%20commitments%20for%20providing%20quality%20and%20equity%20for%20all.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMaharashtra%20and%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20went%20to%20the%20World%20Economic%20Forum%20at%20Davos%2C%20to%20sign%20a%20memorandum%20with%20the%20digital%20coaching%20provider%20Byju%E2%80%99s%2C%20asking%20them%20to%20improve%20their%20curriculum%20for%20secondary%20and%20senior%20secondary%20school.%20This%20is%20notwithstanding%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fncpcr-summons-byjus-ceo-over-allegation-of-malpractice%2Farticle66273971.ece%5C%22%3Echarges%20against%20Byju%E2%80%99s%20for%20malpractices%3C%2Fa%3E%20over%20luring%20and%20misinforming%20parents%20about%20their%20children%E2%80%99s%20abilities%20and%20the%20need%20for%20this%20coaching.%20Meanwhile%20the%20Delhi%20government%20announced%20it%20had%20paid%20a%20%E2%80%98discounted%20price%E2%80%99%20of%20Rs%201%20crore%20as%20the%20first%20instalment%20for%20affiliating%20a%20few%20of%20its%20special%20schools%20to%20the%20most%20expensive%20international%20board%20%E2%80%93%20the%20International%20Baccalaureate.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAnd%20now%20Bihar%20has%20devised%20its%20bizarre%20scheme%20for%20employing%20and%20legitimising%20the%20coaching%20industry%2C%20to%20teach%20its%20senior%20most%20classes.%20It%20is%20also%20luring%20large%20numbers%20of%20its%20unemployed%20into%20this%20business%2C%20without%20any%20qualifications%20for%20being%20teachers.%20In%20one%20manipulative%20stroke%20Bihar%20does%20all%20of%20this%2C%20and%20brazenly%20delegitimises%20the%20place%20for%20professional%20teacher%20education%20and%20the%20critical%20need%20for%20sustained%20long%20term%20investment%20in%20this%20area.%20To%20pay%20as%20per%20the%20lowest%20bid%20for%20one%20class%20%E2%80%93%20where%20a%20specific%20subject%20can%20be%20ascribed%20a%20different%20%E2%80%98%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Eboli%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%99%20or%20call%20out%20rate%2C%20in%20a%20given%20school%20or%20geographical%20area%2C%20is%20making%20a%20farce%20of%20teaching.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOur%20country%20has%20been%20facing%20the%20crisis%20of%20having%20very%20poor%20quality%20teacher%20education%2C%20with%20almost%20ninety%20percent%20of%20its%20institutions%20being%20run%20by%20private%C2%A0%20players%20often%20guided%20by%20grossly%20commercial%20interests.%20In%20fact%20the%20public%20demand%20for%20the%20Right%20to%20Education%20Act%202009%20had%20also%20voiced%20concerns%20that%20governments%20were%20compromising%20on%20quality%20by%20appointing%20various%20kinds%20of%20para-teachers%2C%20or%20unqualified%20and%20low-paid%20contractual%20personnel.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20even%20as%20they%20grandstand%20on%20the%20qualities%20of%20our%20traditional%20gurus%20and%20aspire%20for%20India%20as%20a%20Vishwaguru%2C%20NEP%202020%20and%20the%20NCF%202023%20override%20the%20RTE%20in%20critical%20ways%2C%20closing%20and%20merging%20thousands%20of%20schools%2C%20promoting%20%E2%80%98alternative%C2%A0%20pathways%E2%80%99%20which%20include%20pushing%20children%20under%2014%20years%20into%20open%20and%20distance%20learning%2C%20or%20into%20low-value%20vocational%20courses.%20Now%20diverting%20precious%20public%20funds%20to%20bolster%20commercial%20coaching%20institutes%2C%20is%20like%20sounding%20a%20death%20knell%20to%20a%20public%20system%20that%20is%20accountable%20for%20much%20more%2C%20than%20the%20mere%20%E2%80%9Coutcomes%E2%80%9D%20of%20passing%20an%20examination.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20August%2023%20we%20watched%20a%20serene%2C%20intelligently%20navigated%2C%20elegant%20touchdown%20on%20the%20moon%2C%20and%20acknowledged%20the%20indigenous%20efforts%20of%20scientists%20working%20on%20modest%20budgets%2C%20who%20had%20studied%20in%20smaller%20regional%20colleges%20of%20science%20and%20engineering%2C%20not%20from%20feted%20institutes%20of%20technology%2C%20to%20which%20the%20coaching%20industry%20is%20tethered.%20Witnessing%20the%20moon%20landing%20had%20buoyed%20aspiring%20young%20students%20to%20follow%20their%20footsteps%20in%20science%2C%20hopefully%20to%20also%20give%20them%20some%20alternative%20openings%20to%20plan%20for.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F26110550%2FIMG_2635.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F26110550%2FIMG_2635.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F26110550%2FIMG_2635-300x120.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F26110550%2FIMG_2635-1024x410.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-669939%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22480%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EIllustration%3A%20Pariplab%20Chakraborty%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20strangely%2C%20on%20the%20same%20day%2C%20a%20moonstruck%20National%20Curriculum%20Framework%202023%20ominously%20dispensed%20with%20science%20in%20primary%20school.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENCF%202023%20has%20pushed%20out%20Environmental%20Studies%C2%A0%20(EVS)%20from%20being%20one%20of%20three%20main%20areas%20of%20learning%20at%20the%20primary%20stage.%20Coining%20a%20new%20inconsequential%20name%20%E2%80%93%20%E2%80%98The%20World%20Around%20Us%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%93%20sounding%20more%20like%20a%20book%20title%20than%20a%20regular%20school%20subject%2C%20the%20NCF%20indicates%20this%20as%20an%20informal%20set%20of%20activities%20and%20excursions%20not%20requiring%20a%20textbook.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%20The%20draft%20NCF%20(May%202023)%20said%20that%20teachers%20are%20not%20able%20to%20teach%20EVS%2C%20the%20only%20subject%20which%20integrated%20primary%20science%20and%20social%20science%2C%20because%20of%20it%20being%20interdisciplinary.%20This%20is%20in%20stark%20contradiction%20to%20its%20own%20position%2C%20where%20it%20repeatedly%20promotes%20multidisciplinary%20or%20interdisciplinary%20courses.%20It%20questionably%20places%20the%20onus%20on%20teachers%2C%20to%20throw%20out%20EVS%2C%20because%20they%20are%20unable%20to%20%E2%80%98drive%20discussions%E2%80%99%20about%20the%20social%20environment.%20But%20it%20clearly%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20tell%20us%20how%20teachers%20are%20to%20be%20professionally%20trained%20to%20reflect%20on%20and%20address%20social%20realities.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EThe%20killing%20fields%20of%20Kota%C2%A0%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWe%20are%20everyday%20hearing%20poignant%20stories%20from%20the%20killing%20fields%20of%20the%20Kota%20coaching%20industry.%20An%20image%20last%20week%20of%20the%20institutes%E2%80%99%20buildings%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Frangrez0104%2Fstatus%2F1695988247741296659%3Fs%3D20%5C%22%3Esecurely%20covered%20with%20%E2%80%98safety%20nets%E2%80%99%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%93%20to%20make%20them%20suicide%20proof%20%E2%80%93%20was%20almost%20surreal%20in%20its%20dehumanised%20complacence.%20Who%20would%20have%20thought%20of%20a%20%E2%80%98safety%20net%E2%80%99%20literally%20to%20fall%20to%20this%20deathly%20interpretation.%20The%20police%20mobilisation%20seems%20to%20be%20more%20to%20manage%20%E2%80%98crime%E2%80%99%20prevention.%20Some%20observations%20or%20advice%20by%20counsellors%20attribute%20the%20problem%20to%20the%20mental%20health%20of%20students.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWe%20do%20not%20have%20nuanced%20information%20about%20what%20shape%20the%20bugeoning%20industry%20has%20taken%20and%20why.%20Some%20numbers%20which%20came%20out%20in%20the%20media%20are%20staggering%20%E2%80%93%20of%20the%20centres%2C%20the%20students%2C%20the%20instructors%2C%20the%20rooms%20in%20which%20they%20spend%20the%20entire%20day%2C%20and%20those%20they%20remain%20holed%20up%20in%20at%20night.%20What%20they%20are%20paying%20for%20all%20this%20is%20not%20out.%20Some%20incidents%20of%20parents%20having%20sold%20their%20small%20portions%20of%20land%20or%20indebted%20with%20hefty%20loans%20are%20sporadically%20heard.%20More%20crucially%2C%20what%20never%20gets%20revealed%20is%20the%20dismally%20low%20chance%20of%20getting%20through%20the%20joint%20entrance%20test%20for%20the%20%E2%80%98professional%20education%E2%80%99%20programmes%20in%20engineering%20or%20medicine%2C%20after%20all%20the%20coaching%20they%20go%20through.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20very%20worrying%20development%20is%20the%20market%20unscrupulously%20spreading%20its%20tentacles%20into%20smaller%20towns%20and%20low%20middle%20class%20homes%2C%20where%20parents%20and%20children%20are%20being%20misled%20and%20ensnared%20into%20this%20trap.%20Not%20being%20exposed%20to%20the%20extremely%20challenging%20nature%20of%20these%20entrance%20tests%2C%20designed%20to%20effectively%20eliminate%20the%20massive%20majority%2C%20for%20the%20relatively%20few%20seats%20available%2C%20these%20families%20are%20being%20shown%20false%20scenarios%20and%20pushed%20into%20mortgaging%20their%20assets%20or%20their%20future%20security.%20Without%20an%20assessment%20of%20children%E2%80%99s%20interests%20or%20educational%20grounding%20to%20be%20able%20to%20deal%20with%20the%20entrance%20test%20requirements%2C%20we%20only%20hear%20of%20how%20these%20institutes%20farm%20out%20to%20%E2%80%98counsel%E2%80%99%20families%2C%20almost%20similar%20to%20what%20BYJU%E2%80%99S%20was%20alleged%20to%20be%20doing.%20This%20is%20brazenly%20playing%20on%20people%E2%80%99s%20vulnerabilities%20to%20entrap%20them%20in%20a%20protracted%20and%20losing%20gamble.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMore%20criminal%20is%20making%20young%20children%20helpless%20pawns%20of%20this%20gruesome%20game.%20Pushed%20out%20of%20their%20homes%20and%20secure%20support%20systems%2C%20some%20as%20young%20as%2014%20years%20old%2C%20they%20are%20all%20by%20themselves%2C%20advised%20not%20to%20waste%20time%20building%20friendships%20with%20those%20who%20are%20in%20any%20case%20competitors.%20In%20the%20cruel%20isolation%20and%20taxing%20regime%20of%20preparing%20for%20the%20test%2C%20against%20all%20odds%2C%20they%20feel%20burdened%20with%20the%20moral%20and%20economic%20responsibility%20of%20not%20letting%20their%20parents%E2%80%99%20investment%20go%20down%20the%20drain.%20Not%20knowing%20that%20the%20chance%20of%20that%20not%20happening%20is%20indeed%20minuscule.%20They%20do%20not%20make%20it%20once%20and%20feel%20obliged%20to%20%E2%80%98work%20harder%E2%80%99%20the%20next%20year%2C%20spending%20still%20more%20money.%20But%20the%20cruelly%20extractive%20coaching%20callously%20carries%20on%2C%20knowing%20well%20their%20chances%20of%20not%20making%20it.%20We%20need%20a%20serious%20fact%20finding%20exercise%20and%20rigorous%20study%20to%20look%20into%20these%20practices%2C%20and%20to%20ban%20those%20that%20are%20damaging%20young%20lives.%20How%20can%20such%20dehumanised%20professional%20coaching%20institutes%20be%20sought%20and%20promoted%20by%20our%20government%20school%20systems%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3ETo%20together%20bear%20witness%20to%C2%A0%20Tripta%20Tyagis%20or%20Chail%20Singhs%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cb%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIronically%2C%20right%20now%2C%20in%20Delhi%C2%A0%20University%20we%20are%20shockingly%20witnessing%20the%20planned%20closure%20of%20a%20major%20teacher%20education%20programme%20that%20we%20have%20caringly%20nurtured%20%E2%80%93%20the%20B.El.%20Ed.%20%E2%80%93%20the%20integrated%20four-year%20Bachelor%20of%20Elementary%20Education%20programme.%C2%A0%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOver%20the%20last%20three%20decades%20it%20has%20shown%20that%20investing%20in%20humanistic%20professional%20development%20can%20indeed%20prepare%20sensitive%20good%20quality%20teachers%2C%20curriculum%20developers%20and%20teacher%20educators%2C%20committed%20to%20education%2C%20especially%20for%20those%20being%20marked%20and%20pushed%20out%2C%20on%20grounds%20of%20religion%2C%20caste%2C%20economic%20vulnerability%2C%20gender%20or%20ethnicity.%20A%20centralised%20dual%20degree%20Integrated%20Teacher%20Education%20programme%20(ITEP)%20is%20being%20pushed%20through%2C%20in%20colleges%20running%20the%20B.El.Ed.%20This%20phasing%20out%20or%20%E2%80%98transition%E2%80%99%20as%20it%20is%20called%2C%20has%20seen%20strong%20protests%20from%20college%20faculty%2C%20students%2C%20alumni%20and%20educationists%2C%20but%20the%20government%20seems%20determined%20to%20close%20a%20progressive%20programme%20that%20upholds%20the%20constitutional%20commitment%20to%20education%20for%20democracy%2C%20fraternity%2C%20equity%20and%20liberty%2C%20also%20encoded%20in%20the%20RTE.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWe%20have%20watched%20teacher%20and%20principal%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fmuzaffarnagar-slapping-case-nhrc-issues-to-up-government-police%5C%22%3ETripta%20Tyagi%2C%20of%20a%20private%20school%20in%20Muzaffarnagar%20ordering%20young%20children%20to%20slap%20and%20hit%3C%2Fa%3E%20hard%20their%20sobbing%20and%20distraught%20Muslim%20classmate%20for%20not%20remembering%20his%20multiplication%20tables%2C%20while%20passing%20derogatory%20comments%20on%20his%20religion.%20This%20week%20we%20have%20also%20seen%20%3Ca%2