arrested-8922977%2F%5C%22%3Epolice%20registered%20a%20first%20information%20report%20against%20Gadhvi%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20the%20two%20others%2C%20invoking%20various%20sections%20of%20the%20Indian%20Penal%20Code%20including%20295A%2C%20which%20relates%20to%20acts%20intended%20to%20outrage%20religious%20feelings%20through%20insults.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EDeshGujarat%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported%20that%20the%20two%20others%20were%20also%20released%20on%20bail.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGadhvi%20was%20also%20heard%20shouting%20%E2%80%9Chail%20%3Cem%3Esanatana%20dharma%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%9D%20as%20he%20defaced%20the%20murals%2C%20referring%20to%20an%20interpretation%20of%20Hinduism%20that%20he%20subscribes%20to.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETensions%20flared%20up%20in%20the%20area%20around%20the%20temple%2C%20which%20is%20located%20in%20Gujarat%E2%80%99s%20Botad%20district%2C%20after%20photos%20of%20the%20murals%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fcities%2Fahmedabad%2Fgujarat-murals-in-temples-defaced-man-arrested-8921112%2F%5C%22%3Ebegan%20circulating%20on%20social%20media%3C%2Fa%3E%20last%20week%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3EIndian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20murals%20depict%20the%20deity%20Hanuman%20bowing%20to%20and%20sitting%20at%20the%20feet%20of%20Swaminarayan%2C%20a%2019th-century%20ascetic%20and%20founder%20of%20the%20eponymous%20sect%20of%20Hinduism.%20The%20Swaminarayan%20sect%20has%20a%20large%20following%20in%20Gujarat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20Hindus%20believed%20this%20portrayal%20demeaned%20Hanuman%2C%20who%20is%20traditionally%20seen%20as%20a%20devotee%20of%20the%20deities%20Ram%20and%20Sita.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThese%20individuals%20are%20opposed%20to%20sanatana%20dharma.%20Hanuman%20%3Cem%3Eji%3C%2Fem%3E%20is%20a%20devotee%20of%20Sita%20and%20Ram%2C%20not%20a%20devotee%20of%20Swaminarayan.%20If%20they%20persist%20in%20such%20actions%2C%20we%20are%20prepared%20to%20take%20up%20arms%2C%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D