er%20had%20called%20for%20a%20%E2%80%9Cgenocide%E2%80%9D%20of%20the%20Hindus.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAt%20the%20crux%20of%20the%20political%20battle%2C%20however%2C%20is%20a%20deeply%20rooted%20disagreement%20between%20ideologues%20of%20Hindutva%20and%20social%20justice%20politics%20on%20one%20level%2C%20and%20historical%20differences%20between%20the%20Hindu%20orthodoxy%20and%2019th-century%20reformists%20on%20another.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20Saturday%20(September%202)%2C%20speaking%20at%20a%20conference%20titled%20%E2%80%98%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3ESanatana%20Ozhippu%20Maanaadu%E2%80%99%20%5B%E2%80%98Sanatana%20Abolition%20Conclave%E2%80%99%5D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20organised%20by%20the%20Tamil%20Nadu%20Progressive%20Writers%20and%20Artists%20Association%20to%20critique%20the%20concept%20of%20sanatana%20dharma%2C%20Udhayanidhi%20Stalin%20said%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%E2%80%9CI%20congratulate%20the%20organisers%20for%20calling%20the%20conference%20as%20%E2%80%98eradication%20of%20sanatana%20dharma%E2%80%99%20instead%20of%20%E2%80%98opposing%20sanatana%20dharma%E2%80%99%E2%80%A6%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20are%20certain%20things%20which%20we%20have%20to%20eradicate%20and%20we%20cannot%20merely%20oppose.%20Mosquitoes%2C%20dengue%2C%20corona%20and%20malaria%20are%20things%20which%20we%20cannot%20oppose%2C%20we%20have%20to%20eradicate%20them.%20Sanatanam%20is%20also%20like%20this.%20Eradication%20and%20not%20opposing%20sanatanam%20has%20to%20be%20our%20first%20task%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20continued.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20statement%20triggered%20a%20backlash%20from%20the%20BJP%20rank%20and%20file%2C%20with%20its%20IT%20cell%20head%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Famitmalviya%2Fstatus%2F1697951451333763243%3Flang%3Den%5C%22%3EAmit%20Malviya%20interpreting%20Udhayanidhi%E2%80%99s%20remarks%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20a%20%E2%80%9Ccall%20for%20%5Bthe%5D%20genocide%E2%80%9D%20of%20sanatanis%2C%20who%20he%20claimed%20comprise%20%E2%80%9C80%25%20%5Bof%20the%5D%20population%20of%20Bharat%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EUnion%20home%20minister%20Amit%20Shah%2C%20while%20speaking%20at%20an%20election%20rally%20in%20Rajasthan%2C%20took%20the%20matter%20up%20to%20challenge%20the%20newly-formed%20INDIA%20opposition%20bloc.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20son%20of%20a%20chief%20minister%20%5Ba%20reference%20to%20Udhayanidhi%2C%20who%20is%20also%20the%20son%20of%20Tamil%20Nadu%20chief%20minister%20M.K.%20Stalin%5D%20has%20called%20for%20the%20eradication%20of%20sanatana%20dharma%20%E2%80%A6%20For%20vote%20bank%20and%20appeasement%20politics%2C%20these%20people%20have%20called%20for%20the%20eradication%20of%20sanatana%20dharma.%20This%20is%20an%20insult%20to%20our%20culture%2C%20history%20and%20sanatana%20dharma%2C%E2%80%9D%20Shah%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20DMK%20leader%20quickly%20responded%20to%20say%20that%20his%20statement%20was%20being%20twisted.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CI%20never%20called%20for%20the%20genocide%20of%20people%20who%20are%20following%20sanatana%20dharma.%20Sanatana%20dharma%20is%20a%20principle%20that%20divides%20people%20in%20the%20name%20of%20caste%20and%20religion.%20Uprooting%20sanatana%20dharma%20is%20upholding%20humanity%20and%20human%20equality%2C%E2%80%9D%20Udhayanidhi%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CI%20am%20prepared%20to%20confront%20any%20challenges%20that%20come%20my%20way%2C%20whether%20in%20a%20court%20of%20law%20or%20the%20people%E2%80%99s%20court.%20Stop%20spreading%20fake%20news%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20continued%20to%20say%2C%20before%20adding%20that%20sanatana%20dharma%20was%20%E2%80%9Cresponsible%20for%20many%20evils%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fsouth-india-final-frontier-contest-hinduism-hindutva%5C%22%3ESouth%20India%20Is%20the%20Final%20Frontier%20in%20the%20Contest%20Between%20Hinduism%20and%20Hindutva%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20fact%2C%20the%20Tamil%20Nadu%20minister%20had%20elaborated%20on%20his%20ideological%20challenge%20to%20sanatana%20dharma%20in%20the%20very%20speech%20that%20the%20BJP%20picked%20up%20for%20its%20attack.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CWhat%20is%20sanatanam%3F%20The%20very%20name%20is%20from%20Sanskrit.%20Sanatana%20is%20against%20equality%20and%20social%20justice%20and%20nothing%20else.%20What%20is%20the%20meaning%20of%20sanatana%3F%20It%20is%20eternal%2C%20that%20is%2C%20it%20cannot%20be%20changed%3B%20no%20one%20could%20pose%20any%20question%20and%20that%20is%20the%20meaning%2C%E2%80%9D%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.telegraphindia.com%2Findia%2Fsanatana-dharma-row-exposes-bjps-disconnect-one-election-chanters-who-dont-know-india%2Fcid%2F1963566%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EUdhayanidhi%20said%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20continued%3A%20%E2%80%9CWhat%20did%20sanatana%20do%20to%20women%3F%20It%20pushed%20women%2C%20who%20lost%20their%20husbands%2C%20into%20the%20fire%20%5Bthe%20erstwhile%20practice%20of%20sati%5D%3B%20it%20tonsured%20the%20heads%20of%20widows%20and%20made%20them%20wear%20white%20saris%3B%20child%20marriages%20too%20happened.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EUdhayanidhi%20contrasted%20sanatana%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%9Crigidity%E2%80%9D%20with%20Dravidian%20ideology%2C%20which%20he%20said%20strived%20to%20establish%20equality%20and%20fraternity.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9COur%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Ekalaignar%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20%5Bformer%20party%20leader%20Karunanidhi%5D%20brought%20a%20law%20enabling%20people%20belonging%20to%20all%20castes%20to%20become%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Earchakas%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20%5Btemple%20priests%5D%2C%20our%20chief%20minister%20%5BStalin%5D%20has%20appointed%20people%20who%20have%20completed%20archaka%20training%20as%20priests%20at%20temples%3B%20this%20is%20the%20Dravidian%20model%2C%E2%80%9D%20Udhayanidhi%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CWhat%20did%20Dravidam%20%5Bthe%20Dravidian%20ideology%20followed%20by%20the%20DMK%5D%20do%3F%20It%20gave%20fare-free%20travel%20to%20women%20in%20buses%2C%20gave%20Rs%201%2C000%20monthly%20assistance%20to%20girl%20students%20for%20their%20college%20education%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESince%20the%20war%20of%20words%2C%20Udhayanidhi%20has%20refused%20to%20back%20down%2C%20intensifying%20his%20attack%20on%20sanatana%20dharma%20and%20the%20alleged%20discrimination%20embedded%20within%20its%20doctrines.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAlthough%20the%20matter%20has%20become%20yet%20another%20polarising%20political%20issue%2C%20the%20disagreements%20between%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20Hindu%20nationalist%20politics%20and%20Dravidian%20ideology%20go%20back%20far%20in%20history.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESanatanism%3A%20Ambedkar%E2%80%99s%20view%20contrasts%20with%20the%20Hindutva%20groups%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fncsc.nic.in%2Ffiles%2Freview%2520proforma%2Fselected%2520work%2520of%2520Dr%2520B%2520Rambedkar.pdf%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3ESanatana%20dharma%20is%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eoften%20credited%20for%20defining%20the%20caste%20system%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20in%20India%2C%20allocating%20duties%2C%20occupations%20and%20roles%20to%20communities.%20Critics%20say%20that%20sanatana%20practices%20speak%20about%20eternal%20laws%20but%20in%20effect%20have%20institutionalised%20discriminatory%20caste%20practices%20and%20sustained%20brahminical%20hegemony%20in%20Hindu%20society.%20For%20Dr%20B.R.%20Ambedkar%2C%20Sanatanism%20is%20the%20%E2%80%9Cancient%20name%20for%20militant%20orthodox%20Hinduism%E2%80%9D.%20In%201943%2C%20he%20wrote%3A%20%E2%80%9CThe%20Antisemitism%20of%20the%20Nazis%20against%20the%20Jews%20is%20in%20no%20way%20different%20in%20ideology%20and%20in%20effect%20from%20the%20Sanatanism%20of%20the%20Hindus%20against%20the%20Untouchables.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHindutva%20orgnisations%20have%20invoked%20sanatana%20dharma%20to%20standardise%20Hindu%20identity%20in%20recent%20times%2C%20often%20ignoring%20the%20diverse%20religious%20practices%20across%20India.%20Anti-caste%20organisations%20have%20naturally%20opposed%20such%20standardisation%20by%20Hindutva%20forces%20and%20have%20critiqued%20it%20for%20perpetuating%20casteism%20in%20the%20modern%20era.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fculture%2Findia-culture-hindutva%5C%22%3EWhat%20Explains%20the%20Indian%20Desire%20for%20Homogenisation%3F%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20BJP%20may%20have%20interpreted%20Udhayanidhi%E2%80%99s%20remarks%20according%20to%20its%20own%20political%20convenience%2C%20but%20it%20has%20also%20opened%20a%20pandora%E2%80%99s%20box.%20The%20saffron%20party%20that%20was%20often%20called%20a%20%E2%80%9CBrahmin-Bania%E2%80%9D%20party%20for%20a%20long%20time%20has%20made%20concerted%20attempts%20to%20shed%20this%20tag%20under%20the%20leadership%20of%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHindutva%20and%20anti-caste%20politics%20have%20historically%20remained%20inimical%20to%20each%20other.%20The%20perception%20that%20Hindutva%20is%20inherently%20brahminical%20and%20discriminatory%20had%20kept%20the%20Dravidian%2C%20Ambedkarite%20and%20Mandal%20parties%20away%20from%20the%20saffron%20umbrella%20for%20a%20long%20time.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20Modi%20weaved%20a%20political%20narrative%20around%20nationalism%20and%20development%20that%20could%20supersede%20these%20contradictions.%20The%20BJP%20under%20the%20leadership%20of%20Modi%20has%20taken%20care%20not%20to%20run%20into%20these%20contradictions%20in%20the%20political%20sphere%2C%20choosing%20to%20popularise%20Hindutva%20by%20mostly%20fuelling%20anti-Muslim%20sentiment%20than%20anything%20else.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20fact%2C%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20recent%20victories%20have%20been%20attributed%20to%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20successful%20attempts%20to%20win%20over%20a%20substantial%20section%20of%20OBC%20and%20Dalit%20communities%2C%20for%20whom%20caste%20discrimination%20has%20been%20a%20lived%20reality.%20By%20intensifying%20its%20attack%20on%20Udhayanidhi%2C%20who%20spoke%20against%20the%20inherent%20casteism%20of%20sanatana%20dharma%2C%20the%20BJP%20may%20risk%20giving%20inadvertent%20prominence%20to%20the%20social%20justice%20rhetoric%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Ethat%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fopinion%2Feditorial%2FPluralist-vision-triumphs-in-Bihar%2Farticle59784595.ece%5C%22%3Etrumped%20Hindutva%3C%2Fa%3E%20multiple%20times%20in%20the%20past%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20291px)%2085vw%2C%20291px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F03%2F09101606%2FFqtn1praAAAjfU2-291x300.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22291%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F03%2F09101606%2FFqtn1praAAAjfU2-291x300.jpeg%20291w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F03%2F09101606%2FFqtn1praAAAjfU2-992x1024.jpeg%20992w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F03%2F09101606%2FFqtn1praAAAjfU2.jpeg%201163w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-643324%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22300%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ETamil%20Nadu%20BJP%20chief%20K.%20Annamalai.%20Photo%3A%20Twitt