ioned%20regressive%20practices%20such%20as%20sati%2C%20idol%20worship%20and%20child%20marriage.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Hindu%20orthodoxy%20formed%20organisations%20like%20the%20Bharat%20Dharma%20Mahamandal%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3ESanatana%20Dharma%20Rakshini%20Sabha%20and%20the%20Lahore%20Sanatan%20Dharma%20Sabha%20to%20contain%20the%20growing%20influence%20of%20reformist%20organisations.%20These%20groups%20mostly%20attempted%20to%20homogenise%20%E2%80%93%20and%20even%20standardise%20%E2%80%93%20Hindu%20identity%20according%20to%20the%20doctrines%20of%20sanatana%20dharma.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20BJP%20and%20the%20RSS%20have%20since%20then%20looked%20up%20to%20these%20groups%20as%20mentors%2C%20and%20their%20present%20advocacy%20of%20Hindu%20practices%20resembles%20the%20efforts%20of%20the%2019th-century%20Hindu%20orthodoxy%2C%20despite%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EModi-Shah%E2%80%99s%20political%20outreach%20among%20OBC%20and%20Dalit%20communities.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EReformist%20organisations%20like%20the%20Arya%20Samaj%20and%20Radha%20Soamis%2C%20or%20even%20the%20Ramakrishna%20Mission%2C%20have%20evolved%20into%20different%20entities%20from%20their%2019th-century%20past.%20The%20contradictions%20between%20the%20orthodoxy%20and%20these%20groups%20have%20flattened%20out%20increasingly%20in%20the%20contemporary%20era%2C%20with%20many%20of%20these%20organisations%20finding%20themselves%20closer%20to%20the%20BJP%20than%20any%20other%20party.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EYet%2C%20if%20the%20BJP%20persists%20in%20its%20efforts%20to%20standardise%20Hindu%20identity%20by%20emphasising%20sanatana%20dharma%2C%20the%20historical%20differences%20between%20the%20two%20may%20again%20become%20significant.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESimilarly%2C%2019th-century%20social%20reformers%20like%20Swami%20Vivekananda%20and%20Narayana%20Guru%2C%20both%20of%20whom%20are%20frequently%20invoked%20by%20the%20Sangh%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Eparivar%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20as%20messengers%20of%20Hinduism%2C%20spoke%20and%20acted%20aggressively%20against%20casteist%20practices%20in%20sanatana%20doctrines%20%E2%80%93%20exactly%20what%20Udhayanidhi%E2%80%99s%20criticism%20of%20sanatana%20dharma%20hinged%20upon.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESpeaking%20to%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20the%20author%20of%20the%20recently%20released%20book%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EVivekananda%3A%20The%20Philosopher%20of%20Freedom%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20Govind%20Krishnan%20V.%20said%3A%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CVivekananda%20considered%20the%20social%20and%20economic%20oppression%20of%20the%20Kshatriyas%20and%20Brahmins%20over%20the%20so-called%20lower%20castes%20the%20main%20reason%20for%20India%E2%80%99s%20decline%20and%20downfall%20from%20one%20of%20the%20leading%20civilisations%20of%20the%20world.%20In%20a%20series%20of%20speeches%20delivered%20in%20South%20India%20after%20his%20return%20from%20the%20West%2C%20Vivekananda%20called%20for%20the%20destruction%20of%20all%20caste%20privileges%20and%20of%20untouchability.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbooks%2Fvivekananda-dismissed-hindutva-view-that-blames-foreign-invasions-for-indias-civilisational-decline%5C%22%3EVivekananda%20Dismissed%20Hindutva%20View%20That%20Blames%20Foreign%20Invasions%20for%20India%E2%80%99s%20Civilisational%20Decline%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20had%20a%20huge%20influence%20on%20the%20first%20non-party%20mass%20movement%20against%20caste%2C%20the%20Ezhava%20movement%20in%20Kerala.%20There%20is%20a%20good%20deal%20of%20similarity%20between%20Narayana%20Guru%20and%20Vivekananda%E2%80%99s%20views%20on%20caste%2C%20especially%20since%20they%20were%20both%20vedantists.%20Vivekananda%20seemed%20to%20believe%20that%20caste%20will%20eventually%20disappear%20from%20India.%20He%20says%20caste%20distinctions%20are%20an%20obstacle%20to%20India%E2%80%99s%20progress%20and%20would%20eventually%20disappear%20as%20democratic%20ideas%20advance%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20casteist%20practices%20have%20anything%20but%20disappeared%20and%20remain%20deeply%20entrenched%20in%20even%20present-day%20India%20in%20its%20society%20and%20its%20politics%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cb%3E.%3C%2Fb%3E%20%3Cspan%3EUdhayanidhi%E2%80%99s%20remarks%20have%20gone%20ahead%20and%20drawn%20the%20spotlight%20back%20on%20the%20seminal%20issue%2C%20which%20has%20been%20the%20historical%20reason%20for%20oppression%2C%20violence%20and%20deprivation.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20appears%20that%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20persistent%20attack%20on%20the%20Dravidian%20leader%20was%20also%20forced%20by%20the%20fact%20that%20he%20unveiled%20a%20book%20titled%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ERSS%E2%80%99s%20Role%20in%20the%20Indian%20Liberation%20War%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20at%20the%20same%20Sanatana%20Abolition%20Conference.%20The%20book%20highlighted%20the%20assassination%20of%20Gandhi%20and%20a%20picture%20of%20a%20man%20licking%20a%20shoe%20in%20its%20cover.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20pages%20inside%20were%20blank%20entirely%2C%20where%20Udhayanidhi%20drew%20three%20big%20zeroes%2C%20pointing%20towards%20the%20minimal%20role%20of%20the%20RSS%20in%20India%E2%80%99s%20independence%20struggle%20against%20the%20British.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EDuring%20the%20%E2%80%98Sanatana%20Abolition%20Conference%E2%80%99%20yesterday%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FUdhaystalin%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40Udhaystalin%3C%2Fa%3E%20also%20unveiled%20a%20book%20titled%20%E2%80%98RSS%E2%80%99s%20Role%20in%20the%20Indian%20Liberation%20War%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20page%20depicted%20someone%20licking%20a%20shoe%2C%20while%20the%20second%20page%20showcased%20the%20assassination%20of%20Gandhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20rest%20of%20the%20pages%20were%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FzNq77jYxja%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FzNq77jYxja%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20Siddharth%20(%40DearthOfSid)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FDearthOfSid%2Fstatus%2F1698329219238134196%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3ESeptember%203%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20Gujarat%2C%20the%20faultlines%20around%20sanatana%20dharma%E2%80%99s%20proponents%20and%20opponents%20have%20come%20to%20a%20flashpoint%20in%20Batod%2C%20illustrating%20how%20disputes%20continue%20to%20prevail%20in%20even%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20home%20state%20%E2%80%93%20a%20laboratory%20of%20Hindutva.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdeshgujarat.com%2F2023%2F09%2F01%2Fdistortion-of-hanuman-ji-its-vadtal-swaminarayan-sect-vs-all-other-sadhus-in-gujarat%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EReports%20say%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20the%20controversy%20surrounding%20a%20mural%20placed%20on%20the%20base%20of%20the%20largest%20statue%20of%20Hanumanji%20in%20Salangpur%20by%20the%20Swaminarayan%20sect%20is%20intensifying%20and%20the%20media%20has%20been%20barred%20from%20visiting%20the%20place.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20issue%20could%20be%20more%20problematic%20for%20the%20BJP%20as%20it%20tries%20to%20appropriate%20Ambedkar%20and%20push%20out%20its%20own%20version%20of%20Dalit%20politics.%20One%20of%20the%20most%20influential%20communities%20seen%20as%20supportive%20of%20the%20BJP%2C%20the%20Lingayats%20in%20Karnataka%2C%20have%20also%20got%20complex%20views%20on%20the%20subject.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhen%20coupled%20with%20the%20Rohini%20commission%20on%20the%20sub-categorisation%20of%20OBCs%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fcities%2Fdelhi%2Frohini-commission-examining-sub-categorisation-obc-report-president-8870799%2F%5C%22%3Esubmitting%20its%20findings%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fno-other-body-other-than-centre-can-conduct-caste-census-government-informs-supreme-court-4337183%5C%22%3EU-turn%20by%20the%20Modi%20government%20on%20the%20Bihar%20caste%20survey%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20this%20is%20a%20faultline%20that%20can%20have%20a%20tectonic%20effect%20on%20India%E2%80%99s%20electoral%20politics.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBy%20attacking%20Udayanidhi%20Stalin%2C%20reflexively%20and%20unthinkingly%2C%20the%20BJP%20courts%20not%20only%20marginalisation%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20but%20also%20risks%20tying%20itself%20in%20multiple%20knots%20in%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20country.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693844073000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F04213611%2FUdhayanidhi.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fbjp-attacking-udhayanidhi-stalin-over-sanatana-dharma-remarks%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20concept%20of%20sanatana%20dharma%20was%20given%20shape%20by%20the%20Hindu%20orthodoxy%20in%20the%2019th%20century%20as%20a%20movement%20against%20reformist%20organisations%20like%20the%20Arya%20Samaj%20and%20Brahmo%20Samaj%2C%20which%20questioned%20regressive%20practices%20such%20as%20sati%20and%20child%20marriage.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A63%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fbjp-attacking-udhayanidhi-stalin-over-sanatana-dharma-remarks%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Pulse%20to%20Planet%3A%20'A%20Book%20for%20Future%20Global%20Citizens'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F06%2F17181052%2FGlobe-with-India-II.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDr%20K.%20Srinath%20Reddy%20is%20a%20cardiologist%2C%20perhaps%20India%E2%80%99s%20best%20known%20ambassador%20in%20the%20global%20public%20health%20arena%20and%20a%20prolific%20columnist.%20But%20first%20and%20foremost%2C%20he%20is%20a%20teacher.%20%3Cem%3EPulse%20to%20Planet%3C%2Fem%3E%20published%20by%20Harper%20Collins%2C%20is%20that%20teacher%20at%20work%2C%20breaking%20down%20complex%20concepts%20of%20interplay%20between%20environmental%20factors%2C%20gene%20modulation%20and%20the%20human%20system%20%E2%80%93%20each%20of%20which%20can%20be%20the%20subject%20of%20several%20books%20or%20perhaps%20even%20a%20whole%20library%20%E2%80%93%20within%20the%20space%20of%20a%20few%20hundred%20pages.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20his%20preface%2C%20Reddy%20writes%20about%20how%20inspired%20he%20is%20by%20young%20people%20like%20environmental%20activist%20Greta%20Thunberg%20and%20Nobel%20prize%20winner%20Malala%20Yousufzai.%20The%20book%20is%20written%20for%20the%20future%20Thunbergs%20and%20Yousufzais%20and%20not%20%E2%80%9Chealth%20experts%E2%80%9D%20as%20the%20author%20specifies%20at%20the%20very%20beginning.%20Neither%20is%20it%20meant%20for%20students%20of%20advanced%20biology.%20It%20is%20a%20primer%20that%20distills%20decades%20of%20Nobel%20winning%20scientific%20achievements%20into%20a%20coherent%20series%20of%20cause%20and%20effect%20relationships%20that%20add%20up%20to%20the%20perfect%20whole%20for%20young%20people%2C%20still%20on%20the%20fence%20about%20what%20career%20to%20pursue%2C%20but%20curious%20about%20the%20big%20picture%20and%20saving%20the%20planet.%20The%20author%20attempts%20to%20take%20a%20bird%E2%80%99s%20eye%20view%20of%20the%20vast%20and%20diverse%20system%20that%20is%20simplistically%20referred%20to%20as%20biology%2C%20presenting%20it%20as%20a%20vector%20sum%20of%20multiple%20societal%20and%20political%20determinants%20that%20constitute%20a%C2%A0%20larger%20system%20encompassing%20individuals%2C%20governments%2C%20corporations%2C%20admen%20and%20microorganisms.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20407px)%2085vw%2C%20407px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F04184127%2F61wQa7z0NwL._AC_UF10001000_QL80_.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22407%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F04184127%2F61wQa7z0NwL._AC_UF10001000_QL80_.jpg%20647w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F04184127%2F61wQa7z0NwL._AC_UF10001000_QL80_-194x300.jpg%20194w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-671421%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22629%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EDr%20K.Srinath%20Reddy.%20Pulse%20to%20Planet.%20Harper%20Collins%20(2023).%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOne%20of%20my%20favourite%20paragraphs%20from%20the%20book%20covers%2C%20in%20one%20fell%20swoop%2C%20the%20wide%20expanse%20between%20embryology%20and%20epidemiology.%20%E2%80%9CAs%20the%20foetus%2C%20developing%20in%20the%20womb%20or%20the%20child%20in%20the%20early%20years%20of%20life%20experiences%20undernutrition%2C%20epigenetics%20change%20the%20programme%20of%20the%20body%E2%80%99s%20metabolism%20to%20spare%20the%20limited%20nutrition%20available%20for%20the%20growth%20of%20the%20brain%20and%20nervous%20system%2C%20as%20survival%20depends%20on%20brain%20function.%20Other%20organs%20shrink%20in%20size%20and%20the%20lean%20muscle%20mass%20develops%20insulin%20resistance%20to%20spare%20glucose%20for%20the%20brain.%20As%20the%20child%20grows%2C%20this%20metabolic%20programming%20through%20epigenetic%20controls%20becomes%20counterproductive%20when%20there%20is%20an%20increase%20in%20dietary%20intake.%20Diabetes%20and%20cardiovascular%20disease%20manifest%20in%20early%20adulthood.%20A%20small%20lung%20size%20reduces%20the%20respiratory%20capacity%20for%20exercise%20and%20loads%20the%20dice%20against%20survival%20when%20severe%20respiratory%20infections%20strike.%E2%80%9D%20All%20of%20a%20sudden%2C%20India%E2%80%99s%20second%20wave%20nightmare%20is%20framed%20not%20just%20against%20the%20dominant%20narrative%20of%20infrastructure%20shortage%20but%20also%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fhealth%2Fwhat-are-the-factors-that-impact-child-malnutrition-in-india%5C%22%3Echronic%20malnutrition%20of%20women%20and%20children%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20author%20largely%20steers%20clear%20of%20any%20observations%20that%20might%20raise%20domestic%20political%20hackles%20%E2%80%93%20both%20malnutrition%20and%20Covid-19%20death%20toll%20are%20red%20flags%20%E2%80%93%20but%20he%20does%20delve%20into%20the%20larger%20politics%20of%20healthcare%2C%20choosing%20a%20little%20known%20example%20of%20the%20World%20Trade%20Organisation%20blocking%20attempts%20by%20the%20tiny%20Pacific%20Island%20of%20Samoa%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheconversation.com%2Fthe-strange-story-of-turkey-tails-speaks-volumes-about-our-globalized-food-system-86035%5C%22%3Eban%20the%20import%20of%20turkey%20tails%3C%2Fa%3E%20(73%25%20fat)%20from%20the%20USA%20that%20led%20to%20widespread%20obesity%20and%20diabetes%20in%20the%20islanders.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EReading%20the%20book%2C%20one%20sometimes%20wishes%20the%20examples%20were%20closer%20home%20but%20then%20it%20is%20clearly%20written%20for%20the%20future%20global%20citizen%20with%20diverse%20interests%20who%20transitions%20smoothly%20from%20Barbara%20Streisand%20in%20the%20context%20of%20making%20of%20health%20policy%20to%20biomimicry%20where%20nature%E2%80%99s%20ingenuity%20is%20harnessed%20in%20the%20laboratory%20to%20create%20scientific%20marvels%20such%20as%20airplanes%20and%20ve