ultivation.%20That%E2%80%99s%20why%20I%20chose%20flower%20farming%20over%20wheat%2C%20becoming%20the%20first%20farmer%20in%20my%20district%20%5BFatehgarh%20Sahib%5D%20to%20do%20so%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20he%20grows%2040%20varieties%20of%20exotic%20flowers%20%E2%80%94%20including%20California%20poppy%2C%20gladiolus%2C%20calendula%2C%20alyssum%2C%20chrysanthemum%2C%20daisy%2C%20delphinium%2C%20lupin%2C%20and%20salvia%20%E2%80%94%20on%2022%20acres%20of%20land%20in%20his%20village%20Nanowal.%20He%20produces%20around%2010%20tonnes%20of%20flowers%20in%20a%20five-month%20season%2C%20earning%20an%20income%20of%20Rs%201%20lakh%20per%20acre.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fgurwinder-singh-3-1693544589.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Gurwinder%20grows%2040%20varieties%20of%20exotic%20flowers%20%E2%80%94%20including%20California%20poppy%2C%20gladiolus%2C%20calendula.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fgurwinder-singh-3-1693544589.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fgurwinder-singh-3-1693544589-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fgurwinder-singh-3-1693544589-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fgurwinder-singh-3-1693544589-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fgurwinder-singh-3-1693544589-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-328743%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EGurwinder%20grows%2040%20varieties%20of%20exotic%20flowers%20%E2%80%94%20including%20California%20poppy%2C%20gladiolus%2C%20calendula.%3C%2Ffigcaption